source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000010_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000010_ELIDIBUS<tab>(surpris)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000020_ELIDIBUS<tab>Why am I...? Was it you who called me here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000020_ELIDIBUS<tab>Où sommes-nous...<var 1D /var>? C'est toi qui m'as fait venir ici...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000030_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>On behalf of the Convocation, I bid you welcome to our order.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000030_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Fé<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tions, tu fais désormais partie du Concile des Quatorze.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000040_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>At times you will stand with us. At times you will stand against us. All that you might steer mankind and the very star upon their true course.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000040_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Tu nous conforteras dans nos idées ou tu t'y opposeras, mais toujours pour le plus grand bien de la planète et de ses habitants.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000050_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>For yours is the seat of Elidibus, the Emissary, and by this name shall your every action be guided.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000050_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Elidibus, le médiateur. Bien plus qu'un poste ou un titre, ce nom guidera désormais chacun de tes actes.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000060_ELIDIBUS<tab>So you peered into my memories... No matter. You will have found little of import.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000060_ELIDIBUS<tab>Une vision de mon passé<var 1D /var>? Hmpf, des bribes, tout au plus...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000070_ELIDIBUS<tab>But I see you intended to summon me here no more than I intended to come. The fault is mine.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000070_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tu ne l'as pas sciemment sondé de toute évidence. Ce qui voudrait dire que c'est moi qui ai laissé une porte entrouverte sur mon âme...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000080_ELIDIBUS<tab>Such is the burden of hope...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000080_ELIDIBUS<tab>Mon esprit est encore troublé par ces nouveaux idéaux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Give back Ardbert's body.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Rends ce corps<var 1D /var>! Il ne t'appartient pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Why must you embroil the people in your plans?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Laisse Ardbert reposer en paix, c'est entre toi et moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>What are you plotting?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A1_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Qu'espères-tu accomplir<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000090_ELIDIBUS<tab>What fool would relinquish his weapon on the eve of battle?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000090_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hmpf... Pourquoi m'en débarrasserais-je<var 1D /var>? Il s'avérera bien utile dans l'af<var 16 /var>fron<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment qui s'annonce.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000100_ELIDIBUS<tab>I merely avail myself of such tools as I require for the conflict to come.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000100_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hmpf... Je ne fais qu'utiliser au mieux les outils à ma disposition afin de m'assurer la victoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000110_ELIDIBUS<tab>Come now, my plans are no mystery.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000110_ELIDIBUS<tab>Quelle question... Mon but est pourtant limpide.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000120_ELIDIBUS<tab>That which I do is no different from that which you have done so many times, Warrior of Darkness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000120_ELIDIBUS<tab>Nos actes nous rapprochent plus que tu ne le crois, <var 08 E905 ((Guerrière des Ténèbres)) ((Guerrier des Ténèbres)) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000130_ELIDIBUS<tab>I arm myself. I hone my skills. I make ready to vanquish my enemy─you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000130_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tu t'entraînes sans relâche et t'équipes au mieux pour exterminer tes ennemis. J'en ai fait de même avec ce corps, afin d'éliminer les obstacles qui me barrent la route.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000140_ELIDIBUS<tab>You who have murdered my brothers─who have taken their selfless labors in service to the one true world and turned them to ash.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000140_ELIDIBUS<tab>Lahabrea et Emet-Selch ont disparu à cause de toi... Eux qui avaient lutté si longuement pour recréer notre paradis perdu<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000150_ELIDIBUS<tab>I see you for what you are. You are death, and only in death shall you serve any purpose.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000150_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tu es l'ennemi numéro un du Concile des Quatorze. Et clairement, tu ne te laisseras plus manipuler...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000160_ELIDIBUS<tab>The Convocation charged me to steer mankind and the very star upon their true course. As Elidibus, it is my duty. And I shall see it done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000160_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je me dois d'agir pour le plus grand bien de la planète et de ses habitants... C'est donc à moi, Elidibus le médiateur, qu'incombe la charge de rendre le verdict des serviteurs de Zordiarche.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000170_ELIDIBUS<tab>I will strike you down...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000170_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'exécuterai ton enveloppe mortelle...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000180_ELIDIBUS<tab>Destroy you body and soul. All else must wait.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000180_ELIDIBUS<tab>Puis je disperserai ton âme aux quatre coins du flux éthéré.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000190_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>Destroy you body and soul. All else must wait.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000190_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>Puis je disperserai ton âme aux quatre coins du flux éthéré.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000200_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ere long I will come for you, Warrior of Darkness. And I will save the world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000200_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ta mort est inéluctable, car ainsi seulement pourrai-je sauver l'unique monde qui compte.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000210_ELIDIBUS<tab>One last matter.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000210_ELIDIBUS<tab>Une question pour toi, avant de nous quitter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000220_ELIDIBUS<tab>I bore witness to your final struggle with Emet-Selch. It seemed as if he saw something familiar in you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000220_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'ai eu la chance de voir ton combat contre Emet-Selch dans mes songes... Il t'a confondu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> avec quelqu'un, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000230_ELIDIBUS<tab>As if he mistook you for another.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000230_ELIDIBUS<tab>Sais-tu de qui il s'agissait<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que faites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Hythlodaeus called me his “new old friend.”
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Partager les dires d'Hythlodaeus

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A2_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A2_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Rester muet<var 08 E905 ((te)) (()) /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000240_ELIDIBUS<tab>...No. I recall not of whom he spoke.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000240_ELIDIBUS<tab><var 08 E905 ((Sa)) ((Son)) /var> pas si <var 08 E905 ((nouvelle amie)) ((nouvel ami)) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000250_ELIDIBUS<tab>Keep your counsel, then. You spare me further frustration. As often as we have met, you have never once awakened any memory within me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000250_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tu préfères te murer dans le silence<var 1D /var>? Peu importe. Nos chemins se sont croisés maintes fois, et je ne t'ai jamais reconnu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000260_ELIDIBUS<tab>Mayhap I never knew you. Or mayhap it is another fragment lost.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000260_ELIDIBUS<tab>Nous ne nous sommes jamais rencontrés à l'époque. À moins que cela aussi, je l'aie oublié...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-???-)Ah, I wasn't aware you already had a guest. If the conversation is constructive, I shall not intrude.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-???-)En pleine con<var 16 /var>ver<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>tion à ce que je vois. J'espère qu'elle est constructive...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>But if you seek to stir up trouble, Elidibus, then I must insist you leave at once.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Dans le cas contraire, je te saurais gré de quitter les lieux sur-le-champ...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Argh<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000300_ELIDIBUS<tab>Though you lack Her blessing, your soul is surprisingly dense... Hmph.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000300_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tu ne possèdes pourtant pas la bénédiction de la Lumière... Âme forte ou pas, voilà qui est embêtant si un vulgaire humain peut me résister...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Worry not, I seem to be unharmed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ne t'inquiète pas, j'ai eu plus de peur que de mal.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000320_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Oh, this... This is my own doing─the consequence of my recent exertions.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000320_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ah, ça<var 1D /var>? C'est ma faute, et non le fait d'Elidibus... J'ai trop tiré sur la corde en cherchant un moyen de ramener tes amis dans leur monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000330_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>It is the tower's way of compensating me for the demands I have placed on it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000330_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je fais partie intégrante de la Tour, vois-tu. Lorsque je la pousse au-delà de ses capacités, elle puise en moi l'énergie qui fait défaut.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000340_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Rest assured, it is no great inconvenience at present. Indeed, I told Beq Lugg as much...but they would not be persuaded, and sent me away to rest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000340_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mais n'aie crainte, j'y suis habitué... Pour être franc, ce discours n'a pas su convaincre Beq Lugg. Il m'a jeté dehors avec pour ordre de me reposer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000350_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No need to make a fuss. Strange as it may sound, I consider it something of a badge of honor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000350_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pas besoin de me faire la morale aussi, je te rassure. Plus qu'autre chose, c'est la preuve que je vais de l'avant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000360_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>One of the brave souls who saw me delivered unto the First once said...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000360_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ceux qui m'ont permis de voyager jusqu'ici m'ont confié ces mots avant que je ne quitte mon futur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000370_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>That the world shall ever have a place for tales of heroism, so long as we have need of inspiration in our lives.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000370_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>“Si les légendes ne meurent jamais, c'est parce que nous avons tous besoin d'un peu de rêve et de romantisme dans notre vie.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000380_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Though he and his fellows had no way of knowing whether their mad scheme would amount to anything, they knew that the attempt alone would inspire hope. Or so they hoped.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000380_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>“Voilà pourquoi c'est la réalisation de ce plan insensé, et non nous-mêmes, qui enfantera un nouvel espoir.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000390_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>A more optimistic lot, one would be hard-pressed to find.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000390_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Leur bravoure m'a toujours im<var 16 /var>pres<var 16 /var>sion<var 16 /var>né.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000400_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>They said they would find a means to save our godsforsaken world─just as soon as they had sent me on my way. Said it with such confidence that, for a fleeting moment, I half-believed them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000400_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Sans parler de leur excès d'optimisme. “Une fois là-bas, ce sera plus simple qu'on ne le croit si ça se trouve<var 1D /var>!” “Je suis sûr que tu vas nous régler ça en un claquement de doigts<var 1D /var>!” Ha ha... Tout ça, alors qu'ils n'en savaient rien<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000410_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Such faith, such courage in the face of unrelenting despair. For a long time, it was more than I could bear to remember them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000410_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>À l'époque, je pensais qu'ils conjuraient leur peur en affichant un côté bravache. En retour, je m'inquiétais d'autant plus...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000420_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>But having come this far─having sent full many on their way myself─I see things more clearly.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000420_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mais ces doutes m'ont quitté depuis, car j'ai à mon tour guidé d'autres gens vers un avenir meilleur, et je continue de le faire avec vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000430_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>To take action is to hope. To believe─to <var 1A 02 /var>choose<var 1A 01 /var> to believe is to take the first step towards a brighter future.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000430_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>J'ai enfin vu l'espoir au bout de ce chemin qu'ils furent les premiers à arpenter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000440_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And why do I tell you this? Because I want you to indulge me in a little recklessness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000440_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>À mon tour de n'en faire un peu qu'à ma tête, si tu veux bien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000450_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Needless to say, I have a plan. And...when all is said and done, I will ask yet another favor of you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000450_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous reparlerons toi et moi, lorsque j'aurai accompli mon devoir d'exarque du Cristal.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000460_RYNE<tab>You're both here! Thank goodness!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000460_RYNE<tab>Je... Je vous trouve enfin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000470_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>What's wrong?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000470_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Que se passe-t-il<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000480_RYNE<tab>It's Thancred! He's collapsed!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000480_RYNE<tab>C'est Thancred<var 1D /var>! Il a perdu con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000490_TATARU<tab>Excuse us...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000490_TATARU<tab>Krile<var 1D /var>? O-on entre, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000500_TATARU<tab>This way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000500_TATARU<tab>Suivez-moi, ils sont là-bas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000510_KRILE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000510_KRILE<tab>(concentrée, fait un effort mais est sur le point de lâcher)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000520_KRILE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000520_KRILE<tab>(souffle de soulagement après effort)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000530_KRILE<tab>I would rather you hadn't seen this.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000530_KRILE<tab>J'aurais préféré que vous ne les voyiez pas comme ça. Vous n'auriez pas dû entrer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000540_TATARU<tab>I'm sorry. We have urgent tidings...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000540_TATARU<tab>Pardon, Krile... C'était urgent...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000550_KRILE<tab>No, no, I'm not angry with you. On the contrary.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000550_KRILE<tab>Ne t'excuse pas, Tataru. Je voulais simplement vous épargner un peu de peine...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000560_KRILE<tab>I know full well how hard everyone has been searching for a way to return home. And I had hoped to afford you the time you needed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000560_KRILE<tab>Les Douze savent que vous faites déjà tout votre possible. Ce fardeau n'est pas le vôtre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000570_KRILE<tab>But given our friends' present state, perhaps it was for the best that you came.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000570_KRILE<tab>Et puis, étant donné la situation, vous avez peut-être bien fait de venir me voir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000580_KRILE<tab>Stiff and cold, all of them. As if they were made of wax.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000580_KRILE<tab>Froids et durs, comme si on les avait empaillés, ou réduit à l'état de vulgaires poupées.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000590_KRILE<tab>Barely alive at all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000590_KRILE<tab>Nos amis sont encore en vie, mais ils en frôlent la frontière...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000600_KRILE<tab>And they had been doing so well. Save for occasional signs of aetheric instability, they appeared to be in passable health.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000600_KRILE<tab>Tout allait pourtant bien jusqu'ici. Certes, leur éther vacillait parfois, mais ça n'affectait pas leur santé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000610_KRILE<tab>Then, quite without warning, things took a turn for the worse. A change for which even Master Matoya could offer no explanation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000610_KRILE<tab>J'en ai bien parlé à maître Matoya, mais même elle ne s'explique pas ce changement si soudain.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000620_KRILE<tab>She could only remind me that the soul is yet an unknown frontier, and that much and more lies beyond our ken.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000620_KRILE<tab>Elle m'a conseillé de garder à l'esprit que les mystères de la vie et de l'âme restaient en grande partie im<var 16 /var>pé<var 16 /var>né<var 16 /var>tra<var 16 /var>bles pour nous, et... de me préparer à tout...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000630_KRILE<tab>But let's not lose heart just yet. At times like these, it is all the more important that we remain positive.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000630_KRILE<tab>Souris. Nous ne résoudrons rien en cédant à la panique ou au désespoir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000640_KRILE<tab>Why, I but this moment succeeded in quelling a fluctuation in Thancred's aether.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000640_KRILE<tab>Tout ira bien, j'ai encore le contrôle de la situation. Preuve en est, Thancred vient de me faire une petite peur, mais je l'ai stabilisé en un tour de bras<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000650_KRILE<tab>And while the others have weakened, they have remained relatively stable. I believe I may leave my post for a moment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000650_KRILE<tab>Quant aux autres, malgré leur force vitale qui diminue, je ne m'alarme pas encore.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000660_KRILE<tab>So come, let me hear your tale outside.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000660_KRILE<tab>Continuons cette discussion dehors, si tu veux bien. Nos amis ne risquent rien pour le moment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000670_ALPHINAUD<tab>Forgive the delay.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000670_ALPHINAUD<tab>Désolé pour le retard.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000680_THANCRED<tab>We have visited every region and confirmed the presence of Ascians throughout the realm.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000680_THANCRED<tab>Nous avons eu le temps de faire un tour rapide de Norvrandt. Je vais faire court<var 1D /var>: ce sont bien des Asciens qui sèment la pagaille un peu partout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000690_URIANGER<tab>Lest a grave predicament be made to seem hopeless, it should be noted that they are of inferior rank. The black-masked minions who answer to the red.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000690_URIANGER<tab>J'ajouterais qu'aucun d'entre eux ne porte de masque rouge, marque des Asciens de haut rang.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000700_THANCRED<tab>Yes. A gaggle of schemers attempting to exploit recent events to sow the seeds of petty conflict.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000700_THANCRED<tab>Exactement. Seulement des masques noirs... Ils se contentent d'attiser les querelles nées des incertitudes de la population en ces temps de changement.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000710_THANCRED<tab>Fortunately, nothing of any great concern has come of their meddling just yet.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000710_THANCRED<tab>Aucun incident d'envergure, en somme. Tout du moins pour le moment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000720_ALISAIE<tab>We also encountered a number of the Crystarium's former defenders, busily solving this problem and that in a bid to become Warriors of Light.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000720_ALISAIE<tab>Au fait, on a aussi croisé plusieurs de ces nouveaux apprentis héros. Ils s'attellent à la résolution de tous les problèmes qu'ils trouvent, depuis leur départ de Cristarium.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000730_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Their zeal is to be applauded. 'Tis but a pity I cannot encourage them on their course...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000730_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Voilà qui fait plaisir à entendre. Leur ardeur me réjouit, et j'aimerais sincèrement pouvoir les encourager dans leur entreprise, mais ce n'est pas si simple...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000740_THANCRED<tab>Not knowing Elidibus set them upon it, no. Both the troubles to be solved and the villains to be vanquished are his doing too, like as not.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000740_THANCRED<tab>Car ils jouent cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment le jeu d'Elidibus sans le vouloir. Tout porte à croire que ces “incidents” font partie de son plan, et qu'il pousse les habitants du premier reflet à les résoudre en érigeant le Guerrier de la Lumière en symbole.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000750_THANCRED<tab>And so, with apologies to the aspiring Warriors of Light, I believe it best that we deal with the Ascians quickly and quietly.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000750_THANCRED<tab>Nous devons débusquer nous-mêmes ces Asciens et leur régler leur compte, même au risque de refroidir l'enthousiasme de nos nouveaux aventuriers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000760_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I quite agree.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000760_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Prudence est mère de sûreté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000770_ALPHINAUD<tab>But tell us, what news from the Source? How fare our bodies?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000770_ALPHINAUD<tab>Et de votre côté<var 1D /var>? Comment se portent nos corps dans le monde primitif<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Uh...well enough─though time is not on our side.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>... Tout va bien. Mais essayons de ne pas traîner, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A3_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'm sorry, but...things have taken a turn for the worse.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A3_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Vos corps ne tiendront pas beaucoup plus longtemps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000780_ALPHINAUD<tab>Indeed. Heartening though it is to know we can stay awhile longer, returning home must remain our priority.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000780_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je vois... Merci beaucoup, me voilà rassuré. Nous ferons en sorte de ne pas perdre plus de temps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000781_ALISAIE<tab>This seems an appropriate moment to ask about the spirit vessel. Have you made any progress?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000781_ALISAIE<tab>Plus vite les conducteurs spirituels seront prêts, plus vite nous pourrons repartir. Vous avez fait des progrès<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000790_ALPHINAUD<tab>...Oh dear. Then we must redouble our efforts! Not that we have ever stinted in that regard...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000790_ALPHINAUD<tab>Vous avez raison. Nous devons presser le pas si nos forces vitales s'amenuisent de plus en plus rapidement, et ce, malgré l'aide de Krile et de maître Matoya.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000800_ALISAIE<tab>This would seem an appropriate moment to ask about the spirit vessel. Tell me you've made some progress.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000800_ALISAIE<tab>Plus vite les conducteurs spirituels seront prêts, plus vite nous pourrons repartir. Vous avez fait des progrès<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000810_BEQLUGG<tab>We have, as it happens. One moment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000810_BEQLUGG<tab>Eh bien... oui. Laissez-moi vous montrer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000820_URIANGER<tab>The red stones... Then this doth mean...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000820_URIANGER<tab>Des cristaux rouges greffés aux auralithes... Vous avez donc eu recours à cette méthode<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000830_BEQLUGG<tab>For the benefit of all, permit us to explain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000830_BEQLUGG<tab>Du calme, Urianger. Les autres doivent se demander de quoi il s'agit.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000840_BEQLUGG<tab>As you will recall, using white auracite as our starting point, we fashioned a vessel for mind and memory both.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000840_BEQLUGG<tab>Grâce au potentiel des auralithes blanches et à nos recherches, nous avons développé ces réceptacles, capables de contenir vos âmes en toute sécurité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000850_BEQLUGG<tab>Yet though it served this purpose admirably, the process of imbuing it with one's complete essence proved a somewhat thornier proposition.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000850_BEQLUGG<tab>Qui plus est, désactiver une âme grâce au familier d'Alisaie avant de la transvaser devrait augmenter nos chances de réussite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000860_BEQLUGG<tab>Simply put, the memory would not accompany the mind. And so we looked to the Allagans' mastery of memory transference for a solution.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000860_BEQLUGG<tab>Ne restait plus qu'à conserver la mémoire de la personne, chose dont l'exarque du Cristal est capable grâce à un enchantement qu'il tient de son héritage allagois.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000870_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>This approach was not without its own complications, however, relying as it does upon blood─which inanimate objects notably do not possess.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000870_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, le sang d'Allag doit couler dans les veines de la personne en question.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000880_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>We duly explored methods of suffusing the vessel with drops of the aforementioned. Alas, our painstaking experimentation succeeding only in making me feel faint, and singularly failed to imbue the crystal with the necessary properties.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000880_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous nous sommes bien sûr ingéniés à modifier le sortilège, mais sans succès.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>It was then that an idea occurred to me: namely, that we might fuse the vessel not with normal blood, but with my crystallized essence.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous avons donc pensé à cristalliser un peu de mon sang pour le fixer aux conducteurs spirituels.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000900_ALISAIE<tab>You're doing this for our sakes, so far be it from us to complain...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000900_ALISAIE<tab>Et vous l'avez fait sans hésiter<var 1D /var>!? Je comprends que vous faites ça pour nous, mais je ne sais pas trop quoi en penser...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000910_ALISAIE<tab>But don't think we haven't noticed what's happening to your arm.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000910_ALISAIE<tab>Et puis, regardez votre bras gauche. Vous pensiez qu'on ne remarquerait rien<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>It falls well short of offering up my life in exchange for yours─which was your only stipulated prohibition, as I recall. And it is but a small price to pay for delivering you home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Un prix bien moins cher à payer que ma propre vie, tu en conviendras. Je n'ai aucunement l'intention de vous laisser repartir dépossédés de vos souvenirs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000930_BEQLUGG<tab>Assuming it works.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000930_BEQLUGG<tab>Quoi qu'il en soit, je prie pour notre réussite...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000940_BEQLUGG<tab>We shall soon know if this grisly addition will serve as a suitable conduit for the subject's memory. Though...not soon enough to warrant your waiting. The test is like to take a while.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000940_BEQLUGG<tab>Nous aurons besoin d'encore un peu de temps pour tester notre théorie en intégrant l'enchantement des yeux de rang aux cristaux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000950_THANCRED<tab>Let us be off, then. We have Ascians to attend to, among other things.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000950_THANCRED<tab>À ce compte-là, inutile de nous attarder plus longuement ici. Nous devrions profiter du temps qu'il nous reste, pour commencer une collection de masques noirs, par exemple.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000960_ALISAIE<tab>Forgive me, but I count <var 1A 02 /var>six<var 1A 01 /var> vessels. And there are only five of us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000960_ALISAIE<tab>Au fait, je compte six conducteurs. Ça n'en fait pas un de trop<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>One is for testing purposes. I will personally use it to see whether the crystal functions as it should.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je m'en sers de prototype en le testant sur moi. C'est grâce à lui que je saurai si notre technique est au point.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000980_ALISAIE<tab>And...if it does, wouldn't that mean that your soul could also return to the Source?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000980_ALISAIE<tab>Donc, si on voulait, on pourrait ramener votre âme et votre mémoire dans le monde primitif<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000990_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Yes. In theory, at least.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_000990_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Si ce n'est que ça, oui... Je vois où tu veux en venir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001000_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>But there is a distinct difference between your circumstances and mine. While your corporeal forms want for souls, my past self does not.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001000_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Vous ne devez pas oublier que mon corps dans le monde primitif n'est pas une coquille vide comme les vôtres. Effectuer le même transfert reviendrait à verser de l'eau dans un récipient déjà plein.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001010_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mayhap our essences would blend. Or mayhap they would curdle. There is no telling what might occur.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001010_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nos deux entités pourraient se voir combinées, mais les mystères de l'âme sont bien trop profonds pour que je me hasarde à spéculer sur le résultat.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001020_ALISAIE<tab>And you'd be willing to take that risk?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001020_ALISAIE<tab>Et ça vous va, ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I would.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pour le moment, je ne pourrais rien demander de plus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001040_ALISAIE<tab>I see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001040_ALISAIE<tab>Si vous le dites.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001050_ELIDIBUS<tab>Excellent. I had intended to speak with you alone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001050_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'apprécie ta propension à faire cavalier seul. Je désirais justement te parler sans que nous ne soyons dérangés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001060_ELIDIBUS<tab>None of my doing, lest you misunderstand. The link between her body and soul wavers.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001060_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ah, elle... Je n'y suis pour rien. Le lien qui unit son corps à son âme se dénoue peu à peu. Un vacillement important dans son éther lui a pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment fait perdre con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001070_ELIDIBUS<tab>I know not what you hoped to find here, but it will avail you naught to learn of our past.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001070_ELIDIBUS<tab>Quels secrets espériez-vous percer en venant ici<var 1D /var>? Notre histoire est hors de portée de votre compréhension.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001080_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Reviewing the records yet again? Really? You worry too much, Elidibus.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001080_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Encore en train de passer les notes de ce débat au peigne fin<var 1D /var>? Tu ne penses pas que tu t'en fais un peu trop<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001090_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>This dedication to your duty verges on obsession.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001090_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Quoique, non. Ton excès de zèle prouve surtout le respect que tu voues à ta fonction, Elidibus.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001100_IGEYORHM<tab>(-Convocation Member-)<var 48 F20223 /var>To think some thought you ill-suited for the role. How wrong they were.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001100_IGEYORHM<tab>(-Membre du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Et dire que certains te croyaient trop gentil et indulgent pour jouer le rôle de médiateur. Ha ha ha. De toute évidence, ils se tracassaient pour rien.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001110_IGEYORHM<tab>(-Convocation Member-)<var 48 F20223 /var>But come, turn your gaze outside the window, my friend. The rains have ceased, and we have been graced with another beautiful day.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001110_IGEYORHM<tab>(-Membre du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Regarde donc par la fenêtre. Dehors, la pluie a cessé, et aujourd'hui encore notre belle planète resplendit. La preuve, s'il en est, des bons et loyaux services que tu rends à notre Concile<var 1D /var>!<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001120_ELIDIBUS<tab>It fades. Fades away into oblivion. Does the world no longer have need of me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001120_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je m'estompe peu à peu... N'aurais-je plus rien à apporter à ce monde<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001130_ELIDIBUS<tab>No. I am Elidibus. And I must─I <var 1A 02 /var>will<var 1A 01 /var> fulfill my duty.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001130_ELIDIBUS<tab>Si... Je suis Elidibus... J'ai un devoir à accomplir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001140_ELIDIBUS<tab>Sundered though you may be, you fought for the world's salvation. For hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001140_ELIDIBUS<tab>Même ce héros d'une espèce déliquescente est animé par la volonté d'apporter la salvation...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001150_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hope...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001150_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ainsi soit-il<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001160_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ahhh, it swells within me. Empowers me. Now─<var 1A 02 /var>now<var 1A 01 /var> I may carry out my mission.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001160_ELIDIBUS<tab>Oui... Je sens affluer en moi ses espoirs... sa force... Je vais pouvoir accomplir mon devoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001170_ELIDIBUS<tab>And yet...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001170_ELIDIBUS<tab>Mon devoir...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001180_ELIDIBUS<tab>Why do I yearn for this? Why do I struggle so?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001180_ELIDIBUS<tab>Que voulais-je accomplir déjà...<var 1D /var>? Pour quoi me suis-je si longtemps battu...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001190_ELIDIBUS<tab>I shall take her into my safekeeping. If you want her back, you will do as I ask.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001190_ELIDIBUS<tab>Cette femme sera ma prisonnière, ou plutôt, ma monnaie d'échange.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001200_ELIDIBUS<tab>Show me your strength. I would take your measure.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001200_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je te la rendrai lorsque tu m'auras fait une dé<var 16 /var>mon<var 16 /var>stra<var 16 /var>tion de ta puissance. Nous avons tous deux progressé depuis notre dernière rencontre, et je suis curieux de savoir si te vaincre serait à ma portée aujourd'hui.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001210_ELIDIBUS<tab>I have prepared a suitable arena. You need but ride the flow of aether.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001210_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'ai bâti une arène de circonstance. Laisse le flux éthéré t'y porter. Je t'y attendrai...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001220_ELIDIBUS<tab>You have grown stronger since last we fought.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001220_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'ai ma réponse... Tu t'es amélioré<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> depuis que je t'ai affronté<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> sous les traits de Zenos.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001230_ELIDIBUS<tab>The result of your trials in the First, no doubt.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001230_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ton voyage dans ce monde ne t'aura pas desservi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001240_YSHTOLA<tab>(-???-)Have you finished?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001240_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Voix familière-)La fête est finie. Je n'apprécie guère les canulars de mauvais goût, encore moins les enlèvements.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001250_YSHTOLA<tab>My apologies. I freed myself as soon as I awoke, but rather too late, I see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001250_YSHTOLA<tab>Désolée, tu te retrouves dans de beaux draps à cause de moi. Vous étiez en train de vous battre quand j'ai repris con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce, alors j'en ai profité pour me libérer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001260_YSHTOLA<tab>Now, Elidibus, if you have ceased trading blows, I would trade words with you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001260_YSHTOLA<tab>Tes manières mises à part, tu tombes plutôt bien, Elidibus. Je brûlais justement d'impatience de partager une théorie avec toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001270_YSHTOLA<tab>I have a theory, you see─one concerning that which you seek to accomplish.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001270_YSHTOLA<tab>Elle concerne ton identité et la raison de ta venue dans ce monde. Je suis certaine qu'elle va te plaire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001280_YSHTOLA<tab>It stems from who─or rather <var 1A 02 /var>what<var 1A 01 /var>─you truly are: a primal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001280_YSHTOLA<tab>Arrête-moi si je me trompe, mais tu n'es rien d'autre qu'un Primordial, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001290_YSHTOLA<tab>The ancients created Zodiark to deliver the star from destruction.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001290_YSHTOLA<tab>Souviens-toi. Qu'ont fait les humains originels pour stopper l'apocalypse<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001300_YSHTOLA<tab>If the magick that brought Him forth is the precursor of what we know as summoning, then Zodiark would have been instilled with a presiding desire...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001300_YSHTOLA<tab>Ils ont invoqué Zordiarche grâce à leur magie créatrice, celle-là même à l'origine des Primordiaux. Il leur fallait donc un idéal, un vœu à exaucer. Mais lequel<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001310_YSHTOLA<tab>I found it among the records at Anyder. And it came as no surprise. Were I faced with the world's destruction, I too would wish for the same...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001310_YSHTOLA<tab>J'ai trouvé la réponse à cette question dans les archives de l'Anydre. Face à l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, j'aurais pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment pensé la même chose...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001320_YSHTOLA<tab>Salvation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001320_YSHTOLA<tab>“Je souhaite sauver le monde.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001330_YSHTOLA<tab>I know that you sacrificed yourself to become Zodiark's heart.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001330_YSHTOLA<tab>Les documents que j'ai consultés expliquent que c'est toi qui as servi de noyau. Tu fus le premier à te sacrifier.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001340_YSHTOLA<tab>How you came to be separated from Him is less clear...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001340_YSHTOLA<tab>Pourquoi tu t'es ensuite détaché de Zordiarche, ça je l'ignore...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001350_YSHTOLA<tab>But if you are a fragment of His being, it stands to reason a desire for the world's salvation would drive you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001350_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais le vœu que ce Primordial était destiné à réaliser est resté ta raison d'être. Et plus ce souhait de salvation est partagé dans le monde où tu te trouves, plus tu gagnes en puissance.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001360_YSHTOLA<tab>And thus did you seek to inspire the masses to rise up as Warriors of Light, going so far as to use Ardbert as a symbol of hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001360_YSHTOLA<tab>Voilà pourquoi tu as pris le corps d'Ardbert, pour mieux pousser les habitants du premier reflet sur la voie des héros, sur les traces du Guerrier de la Lumière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001370_ELIDIBUS<tab>Correct on all counts. Such is my nature, and such are my methods.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001370_ELIDIBUS<tab>C'est juste... Je me suis servi de vos héros et continue de le faire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001380_ELIDIBUS<tab>I have aided heroes. I have made them. I have even become them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001380_ELIDIBUS<tab>Parfois en les guidant, parfois en leur présentant un obstacle à surmonter pour mieux les faire grandir. Aujourd'hui, j'en incarne un moi-même, afin de leur montrer le chemin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001390_ELIDIBUS<tab>This served not only to strengthen me, but also to facilitate the work of my brothers, such as Emet-Selch, with his penchant for nation building.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001390_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ainsi, non seulement je deviens plus puissant, mais je camoufle aussi les agissements de mes semblables derrière un écran de fumée. Tout comme Emet-Selch l'a fait en fondant l'empire de Garlemald.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001400_YSHTOLA<tab>Then you will be all too familiar with the fickleness of mankind.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001400_YSHTOLA<tab>(soupire)... Je peux te comprendre. Après toutes ces ères passées à nous côtoyer, tu connais bien l'inconstance de l'humanité...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001410_YSHTOLA<tab>We change. We forget. And what little we do remember becomes twisted and fragmented over time. For which reason, you deem us unfit to carry on your legacy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001410_YSHTOLA<tab>Tu hais nos sentiments changeants, notre histoire lacunaire, notre mémoire imparfaite qui déforme et amplifie. Nous sommes bien les derniers à qui l'on pourrait léguer un quelconque idéal.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001420_YSHTOLA<tab>But are you yourself free of these foibles? As the last witness of the Final Days, do you remember <var 1A 02 /var>everything<var 1A 01 /var> that was lost? Or even the things you cared about?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001420_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais qu'en est-il de toi<var 1D /var>? Crois-tu vraiment être si supérieur<var 1D /var>? N'as-tu pas toi-même oublié ce qui comptait le plus à tes yeux<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001430_ELIDIBUS<tab>Get to the point.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001430_ELIDIBUS<tab>Que veux-tu insinuer<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001440_YSHTOLA<tab>A primal is shaped by the hope that fuels it. Even should this hope be something as simple as the world's salvation, it is the collective desire of innumerable disparate souls crying out for deliverance.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001440_YSHTOLA<tab>La volonté d'un Primordial reflète celle de ses fidèles, et comparé à ton époque, “sauver le monde” a un sens bien différent pour ceux que tu encourages. Comment peux-tu réconcilier ta vision d'alors et la leur<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001450_YSHTOLA<tab>Having drawn your strength from such a cacophony of voices, can you truly be sure you still speak with your own?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001450_YSHTOLA<tab>Penses-tu être la même personne que tu fus autrefois<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001460_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001460_ELIDIBUS<tab>(Ricane)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001470_ELIDIBUS<tab>Your question is irrelevant.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001470_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je n'ai nul besoin de me poser cette question.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001480_ELIDIBUS<tab>No matter how much I should change, no matter how much I should forget, I shall ever remember my duty.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001480_ELIDIBUS<tab>Peu importe que ma conscience se mue... Peu importe que le temps me morcelle peu à peu... Tant que je n'oublie pas ma mission...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001490_ELIDIBUS<tab>At times I stand with my brethren. At times I stand against them. All that I might steer mankind and the very star upon their true course.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001490_ELIDIBUS<tab>Épauler mes pairs du Concile des Quatorze, les ramener à la raison lorsqu'ils font fausse route... Toujours pour le plus grand bien de la planète et de ses habitants...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001500_ELIDIBUS<tab>For Elidibus is my name. And my mission. Guiding my every deed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001500_ELIDIBUS<tab>Elidibus... Ce nom me définit... et il guide chacun de mes actes<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001510_ELIDIBUS<tab>But enough talk. You have shown me sufficient proof of your might.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001510_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'étais venu te mettre à l'épreuve, et c'est chose faite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001520_ELIDIBUS<tab>As I am now, I would struggle to defeat you. Yet I have still to play all of my cards.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001520_ELIDIBUS<tab>La victoire ne me serait pas assurée si nous nous affrontions maintenant... Mais ça n'a aucune importance, car la face cachée de mon plan sera bientôt révélée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001530_ELIDIBUS<tab>If I could offer you some semblance of sport, your lessers would pose no threat to me. Would you not agree, Warrior of Darkness?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001530_ELIDIBUS<tab>Si je fais jeu égal avec <var 08 E905 ((la Guerrière des Ténèbres)) ((le Guerrier des Ténèbres)) /var>, je vous laisse imaginer ce que je peux faire de tous les autres succédanés...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001540_EMETSELCH<tab>Gone is the brilliant radiance of life, replaced by the sickly glow of malformed creatures.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001540_EMETSELCH<tab>Nos âmes morcelées rampent sur terre comme de vulgaires insectes... Où est passé l'éclat de notre monde d'antan<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001550_EMETSELCH<tab>Is this to be how it ends? For we who loved the star with all our being?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001550_EMETSELCH<tab>Ainsi s'achèverait notre existence passée à chérir notre belle planète<var 1D /var>? Dans la déchéance<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001560_EMETSELCH<tab>No. I will not suffer it to be so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001560_EMETSELCH<tab>Non. Pas tant que j'aurai mon mot à dire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001570_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Well, well. We meet again, my new old friend.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001570_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Tiens, tiens. Comme on se retrouve, <var 08 E905 ((ma pas si vieille amie)) ((mon pas si vieil ami)) /var>.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Hythlodaeus.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Hythlodaeus<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>The, uh...receptionist at the Bureau of the Secretariat?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>On s'est rencontrés au bureau du secrétariat, non<var 1D /var>? Vous êtes le réceptionniste<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001580_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>How good of you to remember.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001580_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Heureux que tu te souviennes de moi. Je ne pensais pas que tu me reconnaîtrais<var 1D /var>!<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001590_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Chief of the Bureau of the Architect, in fact. Where I also answered to the name of “Hythlodaeus.”<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001590_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Presque<var 1D /var>! C'était bien là-bas, mais moi, je travaille au bureau des créations. Je suis Hythlodaeus.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001600_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Heh heh... I see you have been collecting stars.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001600_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hé hé... Je savais que ces constellations éveilleraient ta curiosité.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001610_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>I speak of those crystals. They have constellations etched upon them, yes?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001610_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Regarde bien ces petites pierres que tu as ramassées. Des étoiles sont gravées dessus.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001620_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>High in the heavens, those stars shine their guiding light down upon the lives below. Fitting symbols for the Convocation of Fourteen, would you not agree?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001620_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Elles dansent dans le ciel, brillantes et éternelles, et nous servent de guide. Un peu comme le fait le Concile des Quatorze.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001630_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>As you will have gathered, each crystal bears an account of the life of a member of the Convocation as remembered by the unsundered.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001630_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Ceux que vous appelez les Asciens originels en ont créé une pour chaque membre du Concile. Elles renferment des souvenirs liés à ces derniers.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001640_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Lest you worry, they aren't concepts; they are far too incomplete to be so. But they suffice for imbuing memories within sundered souls, that they might be restored to their office.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001640_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hé hé, je te vois venir. Ce ne sont pas des concepts, tout au plus des fragments. Toutefois, elles peuvent se révéler utiles pour raviver la mémoire d'un des Quatorze dont l'âme s'est morcelée.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001650_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Keep them. I am sure Emet-Selch wouldn't mind.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001650_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Emet-Selch n'en aura plus l'utilité. Je te les offre.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001660_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>So, how fare you of late? You are feuding with Elidibus this time, I believe?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001660_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Et sinon, comment vont les choses der<var 16 /var>niè<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment<var 1D /var>? Toujours en train de te chamailler avec Elidibus<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001670_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hm... I shall refrain from passing comment on your struggle. It is not my place to do so, long-departed as I am.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001670_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hmm... Je me garderai bien de commenter votre dispute. Là n'est pas le rôle des morts.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001680_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>But if I may give voice to a personal desire...I would rather you lived.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001680_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Néanmoins, mon espoir, lui, est que tu survives à Elidibus.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001690_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>If you do not, how will you keep your promise to Emet-Selch? The promise to remember?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001690_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Quel gâchis ce serait de nous rejoindre si tôt dans l'outre-monde, toi qui as promis à Emet-Selch de ne jamais nous oublier.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001700_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>It must weigh heavy, the burden of all those memories.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001700_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>C'est un lourd devoir de mémoire qui s'impose désormais à toi.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001710_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>To one who has lived a life such as yours, I can well imagine how Elidibus's existence might seem hollow─how empty his single-minded pursuit of a half-forgotten cause must appear...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001710_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Comparés à cela, Elidibus et ses obsessions doivent te paraître bien futiles.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001720_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>But know that his devotion is not without reason. Even if he himself can no longer remember what that reason is.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001720_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Garde à l'esprit qu'il doit avoir une raison de faire tout cela, même si lui-même l'a oubliée depuis tout ce temps.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001730_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Well, that is quite enough talk about Elidibus. I would see if you can reunite the wayward stars.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001730_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Penses-tu pouvoir réunir ces étoiles déchues<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001740_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>I mentioned before that there was a member of the Convocation who opposed Zodiark's summoning and defected. One whose office was left vacant...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001740_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Je t'avais parlé de ce quatorzième membre qui avait quitté le Concile peu avant l'invocation de Zordiarche, tu te souviens<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001750_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Defectors having been deemed unworthy of commemoration, no crystal exists for the individual in question.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001750_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 08 E905 ((Elle)) ((Lui)) /var> n'eut pas droit à sa pierre. Car pourquoi rappeler à sa mémoire <var 08 E905 ((une déserteuse)) ((un déserteur)) /var> qui laissa sa place vacante<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001760_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...Or shouldn't exist, at any rate─and wouldn't, had a friend not created one in secret.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001760_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Pourtant, la voici<var 1D /var>! Quelqu'un l'aura créée à l'insu de ses confrères...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001770_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>A crystal bearing the forgotten name of <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> office, along with a magick of <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> own conceiving─a singular incantation embodying <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> spirit.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001770_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Elle renferme le nom <var 08 E905 ((de la)) ((du)) /var> quatorzième, ainsi qu'un sort dont seul quelqu'un qui l'a intimement connu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> peut avoir con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001780_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Among all the offices, the Fourteenth was most unusual. For while the rest sat in Amaurot, its holder was charged with gaining an intimate knowledge of the wider world.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001780_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Le rôle du quatorzième membre différait quelque peu de celui des autres. Il devait tout savoir sur le monde et identifier les problèmes qui le gangrenaient.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001790_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>In the course of his duty, he traveled the length and breadth of every land, and befriended countless folk.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001790_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Il menait une vie de nomade et faisait toujours un nombre invraisemblable de rencontres au cours de ses voyages.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001800_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>In the course of her duty, she traveled the length and breadth of every land, and befriended countless folk.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001800_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Elle menait une vie de nomade et faisait toujours un nombre invraisemblable de rencontres au cours de ses voyages.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001810_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 08 E905 ((She)) ((He)) /var> encountered troubles too, of course. Matters which <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> could simply have referred to the Convocation. But that was not <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> way.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001810_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 08 E905 ((Elle)) ((Il)) /var> n'allait pas faire un aller-retour chaque fois qu'<var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> voulait présenter au Concile la source d'un mal, tu imagines<var 1D /var>!<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001820_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Nay, more often than not, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> would call upon <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> comrades, and together resolve matters themselves.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001820_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hé hé. Non, <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> se contentait d'appeler ses camarades, et ensemble, ils l'éliminaient.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001830_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Such is the magick sealed within that crystal─the magick to summon the stars to your side.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001830_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>C'est un sort lui permettant d'accomplir ce petit tour qui est enfermé dans sa pierre.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>In time of greatest need, should you wish upon it with all your heart, it will surely answer your call.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Je suis certain qu'elle te sera utile, devrais-tu faire face à une grande difficulté.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>And now it is where it belongs.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>De retour dans les mains de <var 08 E905 ((sa)) ((son)) /var> pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taire...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Oh, there is no need for thanks. But nor will I hear any complaints about it either.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Inutile de me remercier, au fait. Ce que je t'offre pourrait bien se révéler être un cadeau empoisonné.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001870_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>After all, I cannot say whether I act of my own volition or by the will of my recreator!<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001870_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Après tout, qui sait si j'agis de ma propre volonté ou de celle de mon créateur<var 1D /var>? Je te l'ai déjà dit, je ne suis qu'une ombre désincarnée, une illusion<var 1D /var>!<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001880_YSHTOLA<tab>I was wondering where you had disappeared to.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001880_YSHTOLA<tab>Ah, tu étais là. Je t'ai cherché<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> partout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001890_YSHTOLA<tab>Is something troubling you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001890_YSHTOLA<tab>Il t'est arrivé quelque chose<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001900_YSHTOLA<tab>...No? Very well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001900_YSHTOLA<tab>Hmm... Si tu le dis...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001910_YSHTOLA<tab>I have everything. Let's hurry back to the surface.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001910_YSHTOLA<tab>De mon côté, j'ai fini de récupérer tout mon fourbi. Que dirais-tu de rentrer<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001920_YSHTOLA<tab>Forgive us our lateness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001920_YSHTOLA<tab>Nous revoilà.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001930_YSHTOLA<tab>Master Chai, my congratulations on your appointment. By all accounts, you are a capable mayor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001930_YSHTOLA<tab>Monsieur Chai, voilà longtemps qu'on ne s'était pas vus. Mes félicitations pour votre élection.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001940_CHAINUZZ<tab>Oh, I have capable friends, my lady. I must say, it's good to see you looking hale and whole again.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001940_CHAINUZZ<tab>Merrrci beaucoup, elle n'aurait pu se faire sans votre aide à vous tous. Je suis ravi de vous retrouver en pleine forme.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001950_YSHTOLA<tab>The credit for that lies with my own capable friend, without whom I might never have escaped my abductor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001950_YSHTOLA<tab>Hmpf<var 1D /var>! Fraîchement évanouie, capturée puis libérée, mais en pleine forme grâce à notre ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, oui.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001960_THANCRED<tab>A primal... I suppose that would explain why Elidibus has been fostering faith in the Warrior of Light.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001960_THANCRED<tab>Elidibus... un Primordial<var 1D /var>? Et il vante les mérites du Guerrier de la Lumière afin d'acquérir plus de puissance...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001970_THANCRED<tab>While you were enjoying your audience with the wandering heart of Zodiark, we were busy dispatching the last of the black-masked Ascians. A task which proved almost insultingly easy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001970_THANCRED<tab>Inquiétant, mais au moins, on y voit plus clair. Nous savons maintenant pourquoi tous les Asciens à masque noir que nous avons croisés étaient si faciles à battre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001980_THANCRED<tab>Formidable though we undoubtedly are, they were obviously sent to provide encouragement for budding heroes. One cannot help but wonder how many times the ploy has been used before...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001980_THANCRED<tab>Elidibus jouait donc bien les agitateurs pour que les gens vouent une sorte de culte au Guerrier de la Lumière... C'est à se demander combien de fois il a utilisé ce stratagème.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001990_ALPHINAUD<tab>Master Chai, you mentioned that the people of Kholusia are similarly enamored of the Warrior of Light.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_001990_ALPHINAUD<tab>Monsieur Chai, que me disiez-vous un peu plus tôt<var 1D /var>? À propos des rumeurs qui courent à Kholusia sur le Guerrier de la Lumière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002000_CHAINUZZ<tab>Indeed. Though it's hardly surprising given the state of the world. Many are still struggling to find a purpose, and it's only natural that they should take comfort in the tales.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002000_CHAINUZZ<tab>Qu'elles vont bon trrrain... À Eulmore plus qu'ailleurs, de nombreuses personnes s'interrogent sur leur avenir. S'ils s'en voient proposer un, ils n'y réfléchiront pas à deux fois avant de le saisir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002010_ALPHINAUD<tab>Then the fever has spread to every corner of Norvrandt.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002010_ALPHINAUD<tab>Elidibus a donc pour ainsi dire fini son tour de Norvrandt...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002020_ALPHINAUD<tab>We may have dealt with his black-masked minions, but it is plain Elidibus has yet to show his hand.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002020_ALPHINAUD<tab>Que compte-t-il faire maintenant que nous avons vaincu ses sbires<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002030_DULIACHAI<tab>Oh my, what a spectacular sky!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002030_DULIACHAI<tab>Oh<var 1D /var>! Regardez-moi ce ciel<var 1D /var>! Quel magnifique et étrrrange spectacle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002040_ALISAIE<tab>Another starshower...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002040_ALISAIE<tab>Encore cette illusion<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002050_RYNE<tab>Wait, is that...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002050_RYNE<tab>Pas tout à fait<var 1D /var>! Regardez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002060_RYNE<tab>...Amaurot?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002060_RYNE<tab>On dirait... Amaurote<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002070_EULMOREMANA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002070_EULMOREMANA<tab>(Léger mal de tête)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002075_HYDAELYN<tab>Hear... Feel... Think...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002075_HYDAELYN<tab>Entends... Ressens... Pense...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002080_EULMOREMANA<tab>Did you hear that? That voice, calling out...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002080_EULMOREMANA<tab>Hé. J'suis le seul à avoir entendu comme une voix<var 1D /var>? J'ai l'impression qu'elle me parlait...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002090_EULMOREMANB<tab>No, I didn't hear anything. But...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002090_EULMOREMANB<tab>Je l'ai entendue, moi aussi... Mais j'ai rien compris...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002100_EULMOREMANB<tab>Why do I feel so... Like I've lost something dear to me...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002100_EULMOREMANB<tab>Je sais pas ce qu'elle disait, mais... pourquoi... pourquoi suis-je si triste tout à coup...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002110_ALPHINAUD<tab>Does Elidibus seek to awaken more people to the Echo with clearer visions of the Final Days?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002110_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ce serait ça, la suite du plan d'Elidibus<var 1D /var>? Des visions encore plus réalistes pour convertir plus efficacement les gens<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002120_WARRIOROFLIGHTAVATARS<tab>In the name...of the Light...I shall vanquish...the Darkness...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002120_WARRIOROFLIGHTAVATARS<tab>La Lumière nous guide. Ensemble, nous dissiperons le voile des Ténèbres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002130_WARRIOROFLIGHTAVATARS<tab>I shall deliver the world from its doom!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002130_WARRIOROFLIGHTAVATARS<tab>Et ramènerons paix et félicité sur notre monde<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002140_THANCRED<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002140_THANCRED<tab>(Contre un coup puissant avec son épée)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002150_THANCRED<tab>And who might you be!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002150_THANCRED<tab>D'où tu sors, toi<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002160_ALISAIE<tab>Whoever they are, they've come for our heads!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002160_ALISAIE<tab>Ils en ont après nous<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002170_ALISAIE<tab>No you don't!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002170_ALISAIE<tab>Même pas en rêve<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002180_ALISAIE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002180_ALISAIE<tab>(Frappe avec la pointe de son épée)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002190_YSHTOLA<tab>They are not of flesh and blood.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002190_YSHTOLA<tab>Des apparitions immatérielles...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002200_URIANGER<tab>I know this magick.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002200_URIANGER<tab>Nous nous sommes peut-être fait damer le pion...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002210_URIANGER<tab>The rings are like unto those that the Exarch did employ in our summoning.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002210_URIANGER<tab>Ces cercles magiques sont identiques à ceux qu'emploie l'exarque.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002220_THANCRED<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002220_THANCRED<tab>(Coup final pour se débarrasser d'un ennemi)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002230_THANCRED<tab>Are you saying the Exarch is summoning them?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002230_THANCRED<tab>Tu veux dire que c'est lui qui les fait venir d'un autre monde<var 1D /var>? T'es pas sérieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002240_URIANGER<tab>Nay. Yet the similarity can be no mere coincidence...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002240_URIANGER<tab>C'est ce qu'il semble à en juger par le rituel, mais ça n'a aucun sens... Une diversion<var 1D /var>? Un piège<var 1D /var>? Les deux à la fois...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002250_RYNE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002250_RYNE<tab>(Abat un ennemi d'un seul coup)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002260_RYNE<tab>Should we make a stand here? Or retreat to the Crystarium?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002260_RYNE<tab>Qu'est-ce qu'on fait<var 1D /var>!? On rentre à Cristarium<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002270_YSHTOLA<tab>The aether churns around us. More of them will appear ere long.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002270_YSHTOLA<tab>Le flux éthéré est perturbé... D'autres ne vont pas tarder à arriver pour finir le travail.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002280_YSHTOLA<tab>To stay would only place innocents in harm's way. We must fight this battle elsewhere.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002280_YSHTOLA<tab>Nous risquons de mettre en danger les Eulmoriens si nous restons ici. Sortons de la ville et trouvons un endroit désert.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002290_CHAINUZZ<tab>Wait!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002290_CHAINUZZ<tab>Attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002300_CHAINUZZ<tab>Take one of our airships! You can decide what to do on your flight to the Crystarium!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002300_CHAINUZZ<tab>Vous rejoindrrrez Cristarium bien plus rapidement par la voie des airs<var 1D /var>! Prenez un de nos aéronefs, et profitez du trajet pour préparer votre contre-attaque<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002310_YSHTOLA<tab>You are a capable leader in your own right, Master Chai. The citizens of Eulmore chose well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002310_YSHTOLA<tab>Votre âme de meneur brille même dans les pires situations, Monsieur Chai. Vous pouvez compter sur nos voix lors des prochaines élections.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002320_ALPHINAUD<tab>It's settled, then. To the airship!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002320_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tout le monde à l'embarcadère<var 1D /var>! Vite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002330_RYNE<tab>I think that's the last of them...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002330_RYNE<tab>On en est enfin venus à bout, on dirait...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002340_THANCRED<tab>Apparently, even they have limits. Nevertheless, we should remain vigilant.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002340_THANCRED<tab>Je n'y croyais plus... Mais ne crions pas victoire trop tôt.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002350_ALISAIE<tab>Urianger, something occurred to me while we were fighting. These enemies...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002350_ALISAIE<tab>Urianger... Toi aussi, tu as remarqué le point commun entre nos adversaires, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002360_URIANGER<tab>...Are heroes hailing from other shards, summoned hither to deliver this world from its doom.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002360_URIANGER<tab>Oui... Ils semblaient se battre pour le salut de leur monde. Nous avons pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment eu affaire aux héros d'autres reflets...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002370_URIANGER<tab>Scant moments after the starshower did they appear─as yet more souls were inspired to walk the hero's path, no doubt.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002370_URIANGER<tab>Qui plus est, leur apparition coïncide avec cette nouvelle illusion de l'apocalypse amaurotaine, qui a aussi enhardi bien d'autres habitants de Norvrandt... Les deux phénomènes doivent être liés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002380_URIANGER<tab>Thus did hopes for salvation of realms near and far resonate and converge...lending still greater strength unto our adversary.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002380_URIANGER<tab>Par delà les mondes, l'humanité est en ce moment unie autour d'un vœu de salut. Et cela profite à une personne en particulier.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002390_ALISAIE<tab>So that's Elidibus's game. But first things first: if the rings are the same as the Exarch's, then we need to ask him how that's possible.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002390_ALISAIE<tab>Elidibus... Comme tu le disais, le rituel d'invocation ressemble à celui qui nous a fait venir dans le premier reflet... Ça implique que l'exarque est pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment en danger.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002400_ALPHINAUD<tab>The Crystarium is close. Let us press on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002400_ALPHINAUD<tab>Le soutien de tous nos amis nous a rapprochés de notre but. Ne les décevons pas, et profitons de l'accalmie pour rejoindre Cristarium le plus vite possible<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002410_YSHTOLA<tab>They come!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002410_YSHTOLA<tab>Attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002420_THANCRED<tab>So near and yet so far.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002420_THANCRED<tab>Quand y en plus, y en a encore...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002430_RYNE<tab>“In the chaos of conflict, one can always find an opening to exploit.”
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002430_RYNE<tab>Lorsqu'on est surpassé en nombre, il faut semer la confusion dans les rangs ennemis pour créer une ouverture.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002440_THANCRED<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002440_THANCRED<tab>(petit rire bref)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002450_THANCRED<tab>Whoever taught you that is a wise man indeed. And good with a gunblade. But yes, I daresay we can create an opening wide enough for at least one of us to slip through.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002450_THANCRED<tab>Tu m'ôtes les mots de la bouche. Si on se débrouille bien, quelqu'un pourra percer à travers eux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002460_THANCRED<tab>That being you, of course─though others are welcome to follow in your wake. Ryne and I will keep our guests occupied.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002460_THANCRED<tab>Et ce quelqu'un, ce sera toi<var 1D /var>! Fonce dès qu'on t'aura ouvert le chemin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002470_YSHTOLA<tab>Brave and selfless as ever. Yet the two of you may struggle to fool our foes, aetherically sensitive as they are.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002470_YSHTOLA<tab>Quelle vaillance. Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, à vous deux vous ne duperez pas les mages et leur vision de l'éther.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002480_YSHTOLA<tab>Had you a comrade who could use destructive magicks to wreak havoc upon the ambient aether, on the other hand...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002480_YSHTOLA<tab>À moins de les aveugler en déchaînant des sorts offensifs assez puissants pour perturber le flux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002490_URIANGER<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002490_URIANGER<tab>(petit rire satisfait)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002500_URIANGER<tab>Very well, I too shall assist in the diversionary effort.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002500_URIANGER<tab>Vous pouvez compter sur moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002510_ALISAIE<tab>Oh, not this old dance again... Yes. Obviously, I'll stay and fight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002510_ALISAIE<tab>Voilà un plan qui me plaît<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002520_ALISAIE<tab>Alphinaud! I'm about to do a great many stupid and reckless things. Watch my back, would you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002520_ALISAIE<tab>Je vais mettre la dose, Alphinaud. Alors occupe-toi de nous soigner au besoin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002530_ALPHINAUD<tab>And there you have it. Take care of yourself, my friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002530_ALPHINAUD<tab>Vous l'avez entendue... Je ferai de mon mieux aussi. Soyez prudent<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> de votre côté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Make it a nice big opening, eh!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je compte sur vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>You don't have enough lives for this...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Allez-y mollo sur la magie, tout de même.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Use your magic sparingly, do you hear?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A5_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je ne peux pas vous laisser comme ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002540_RYNE<tab>We'll do our best!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002540_RYNE<tab>On donnera tout ce qu'on a<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002550_YSHTOLA<tab>Rest assured I have no intention of expending any of mine this day.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002550_YSHTOLA<tab>C'est d'accord, mais je ne promets rien pour les autres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002560_ALPHINAUD<tab>I shall not overexert myself without good reason. As for the others...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002560_ALPHINAUD<tab>Faites-moi confiance. Vous nous retrouverez tous sans la moindre égratignure, ou presque<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002570_ALISAIE<tab>Finished? Then let's begin!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002570_ALISAIE<tab>Allez<var 1D /var>! C'est moi qui ouvre le bal<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002580_ALISAIE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002580_ALISAIE<tab>(Lance son sort le plus puissant, comme si elle le dirigeait avec les deux mains)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002590_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>A short while earlier, in the Ocular...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002590_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Un peu plus tôt, dans la Tour de Cristal

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002600_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>...'Tis done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002600_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>On a réussi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002610_BEQLUGG<tab>Let me see! Let me see!
