target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002610_BEQLUGG<tab>Oooh<var 1D /var>! Montrez-moi ça<var 1D /var>! Je veux voir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002620_BEQLUGG<tab>Yes! Your memories are preserved safely within! We've done it! We've done it at last!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002620_BEQLUGG<tab>Ohhh<var 1D /var>! Vous avez raison<var 1D /var>! Je peux sentir votre mémoire, intacte<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002630_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002630_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(soupire de soulagement)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002640_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I have inspected the other vessels. They are all ready to receive of our friends' memories.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002640_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>J'ai enchanté de la même façon les cinq autres. Ils fonctionneront tout aussi bien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002650_BEQLUGG<tab>Excellent, excellent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002650_BEQLUGG<tab>Quelle bonne nouvelle<var 1D /var>! Nous devons prévenir vos amis au plus vite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002660_BEQLUGG<tab>I shall have my familiars bear word to them at once!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002660_BEQLUGG<tab>Attendez une petite seconde, j'ai un familier qui fera par<var 16 /var>fai<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment l'affaire<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002670_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Elidibus...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002670_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Elidibus<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002680_ELIDIBUS<tab>It was not until I observed the battle between Emet-Selch and the Warrior of Darkness that I realized what I must do.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002680_ELIDIBUS<tab>Un plan a germé dans mon esprit, lorsque j'ai eu cette vision fortuite de la fin d'Emet-Selch.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002690_ELIDIBUS<tab>I will summon heroes from other worlds unto the First, just as you did.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002690_ELIDIBUS<tab>Si l'exarque peut appeler les héros d'autres mondes pour qu'ils se battent aux côtés <var 08 E905 ((de la Guerrière des Ténèbres)) ((du Guerrier des Ténèbres)) /var>, pourquoi ne pourrais-je pas en faire autant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002700_ELIDIBUS<tab>Their presence shall serve to empower me─granting me the strength to crush my enemy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002700_ELIDIBUS<tab>Malgré le désir de salvation du premier reflet, je manque encore de force pour vaincre mon adversaire. Mais il plierait tel un fétu de paille face au souhait de l'humanité tout entière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002710_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Though it pains me to disappoint you, I feel compelled to explain that the magick in question requires no small amount of preparation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002710_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment pour toi, les longs préparatifs que requiert ce sort d'invocation risquent de mettre un frein à tes ambitions.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002720_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ah, but you assume I require my champions to be summoned in their entirety. I do not. Their souls needn't even be whole.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002720_ELIDIBUS<tab>Une forme incomplète fera par<var 16 /var>fai<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment l'affaire, leur corps ne m'est d'aucune utilité. À vrai dire, je n'ai même pas besoin que leur âme entière fasse la traversée comme celles de tes amis Héritiers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002730_ELIDIBUS<tab>My purpose requires no more than their burning desire to vanquish evil.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002730_ELIDIBUS<tab>Cet instant fugace avant la bataille, où l'envie de vaincre le mal brûle au plus fort dans leur cœur... Voilà l'état d'esprit dont j'ai besoin, la seule chose dont j'empreindrai l'éther.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002740_ELIDIBUS<tab>This I shall sear upon the aether, raising thereby an army of phantom heroes, to whom I shall whisper, as I have to so many over the ages...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002740_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ensuite, comme je l'ai déjà fait durant des milliers d'années, je m'insinuerai dans l'esprit de ces fragments de héros et leur susurrerai ces quelques mots<var 1D /var>:

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002750_ELIDIBUS<tab>“Here lies darkness. It must be destroyed.”
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002750_ELIDIBUS<tab>“Tu as sous tes yeux l'incarnation des Ténèbres. À toi de l'occire.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002760_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And you expect me to cooperate?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002760_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tu ne crois tout de même pas que je vais t'aider<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002770_ELIDIBUS<tab>I do not require your cooperation. Your death will suffice. The magick, I shall have from your corpse.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002770_ELIDIBUS<tab>Non... Je vais te tuer, puis je m'approprierai ton corps et le sang ensorcelé qu'il contient.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002780_BEQLUGG<tab>Go, Lugus!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002780_BEQLUGG<tab>À moi<var 1D /var>! Lugus<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002790_BEQLUGG<tab>We must flee!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002790_BEQLUGG<tab>Fuyez<var 1D /var>! Vite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002800_BEQLUGG<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002800_BEQLUGG<tab>(subit un coup)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002810_ELIDIBUS<tab>...But what is this?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002810_ELIDIBUS<tab>Tiens, tiens...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002820_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-???-)Argh... Unnngh...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002820_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-???-)Rhaaa... Argh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002830_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>My friend... How did you...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002830_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Toi<var 1D /var>? Ici<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002840_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No matter... Elidibus... He took us unawares...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002840_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>E-Elidibus nous a attaqués... Nous nous sommes défendus du mieux que nous pouvions, mais voilà le résultat...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002850_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002850_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(Cri un peu retenu, la douleur reprend de plus belle)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002860_BEQLUGG<tab>It was all we could do...to raise a ward to hinder his steps... And so we fled...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002860_BEQLUGG<tab>Nous avions peu de chance de le vaincre... même à deux<var 1D /var>! Alors... nous avons dressé une barrière pour le retenir... et fui... grâce à un sort de téléportation...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002870_BEQLUGG<tab>But he took it... The vessel with the Exarch's memories...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002870_BEQLUGG<tab>Il... Il nous a volé le conducteur spirituel qui contenait la mémoire de l'exarque...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002880_BEQLUGG<tab>Forgive me... Forgive me...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002880_BEQLUGG<tab>Pardonnez-moi... Pardonnez-moi...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>The vessel bears not only my memories, but my blood─the blood of Allagan royalty...granting him the means to control the tower.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>J'ai achevé cet appareil en y incorporant un peu de mon sang. Non seulement il contient ma mémoire, mais il porte aussi la marque de la noblesse d'Allag. Elidibus a en sa possession tout ce qu'il faut pour contrôler la Tour de Cristal...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>With it, he has performed I know not how many summonings, calling forth heroes from across the rift.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Il... Il a invoqué des héros d'autres mondes... pour te vaincre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002910_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And as you can see, the burden upon the tower is beginning to tell...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002910_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Il ne ménage pas la Tour... Je ressens son agonie au plus profond de moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Leave him to me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>... Reposez-vous, maintenant. Je m'occupe de tout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'm just glad you're alive. Make sure you stay that way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Vous êtes en vie, c'est ce qui compte.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No. I won't let you go alone. Not this time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ohhh que non.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002930_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>If you mean to face him alone, I will not allow it. Not this time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002930_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pas tout à fait... Ce qui compte... c'est que je tienne encore sur mes jambes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002940_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002940_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(Ressent de la douleur en se relevant)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002950_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Elidibus has exploited the people's nobility. Twisted their purest intentions for terrible ends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002950_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Elidibus manipule les êtres humains... et l'image de leurs héros... Chaque main tendue, chaque aspiration... Il les détourne dans le seul but de nous meurtrir...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002960_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And I cannot let it stand. As Exarch, it is my duty to protect them. To defend their hopes and dreams.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002960_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>C'est à moi de l'arrêter... Parce que je suis l'exarque du Cristal... Parce que je défends nos rêves et nos espoirs...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>So I'm going to the Crystal Tower, with or without your blessing─though I would rather it were with.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Aide-moi à regagner la Tour<var 1D /var>! Je t'en prie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002980_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Thank you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002980_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je te remercie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002990_BEQLUGG<tab>I'd join you...but I would only be a burden. Better that I remain here with my gremlins...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_002990_BEQLUGG<tab>J'aurais bien du mal... à lever ne serait-ce que le petit doigt... Laissez-moi ici... Les quolibets des gremlins... ne me tueront pas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003000_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I shall send help. Stay strong, my friend, and take heart.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003000_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous vous enverrons de l'aide, Beq Lugg. Et quoi qu'il arrive, rassurez-vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003010_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>By binding Elidibus within the tower, we have done more than simply delay him.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003010_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>La barrière que vous m'avez aidé à ériger nous a permis d'emprisonner temporairement Elidibus dans la Tour, mais pas seulement.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003020_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Much like our adversary, I am not wont to show my hand prematurely. But the time has come to bring my strongest card to bear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003020_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tu dois le savoir maintenant, je garde toujours un atout dans ma manche. Le moment de l'abattre est presque venu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>To the tower!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Allons-y<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003040_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Not here either. We must keep climbing.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003040_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Aucun signe de lui... Il doit être plus haut<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003050_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003050_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(Cri sourd.)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003060_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003060_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(Cri de douleur après s'être écroulé)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003070_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>'Twas but a matter of time...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003070_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Évidemment... Il sait où on se trouve...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003080_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I cannot keep up with you. Nor will it avail us to make a stand here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003080_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Fini la course pour moi... Plus je te ferai perdre de temps, plus tu devras affronter d'invocations, et plus elles draineront tes forces.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003090_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>You must go on without me. Find Elidibus, and stop him.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003090_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pars devant, s'il te plaît... Elidibus est encore plus haut. Trouve-le et arrête-le<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003100_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Worry not, my friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003100_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ne t'en fais pas pour moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003110_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Though I am no warrior, I have learned to hold my own over the years.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003110_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>C'est toi qui as le travail le plus difficile. Et puis, ça aura mis le temps, mais je suis plus dégourdi que lorsqu'on s'est rencontrés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003120_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>When first we explored this tower, you and your fellow adventurers formed the van, while I was left to follow in your wake.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003120_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tu te souviens quand on a exploré la Tour pour la première fois<var 1D /var>? Toi et tes amis aviez pris les devants, tandis que j'avais dû me contenter d'assurer vos arrières...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003130_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Suffice it to say, I was not best pleased with the arrangement. How I wished that I could join you...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003130_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Il a bien fallu que je ronge mon frein... Mais je n'avais qu'un seul désir, c'était de partir à l'aventure avec vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003140_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And now I have, here where it all began.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003140_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Aujourd'hui, il s'est enfin réalisé. Alors, je ne regrette plus rien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003150_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I was right to trust in you and the power of your legacy─of your name. To let them guide my every deed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003150_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tu es mon exemple... Tu me définis et guides chacun de mes actes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003160_ELIDIBUS<tab>For Elidibus is my name. And my mission. Guiding my every deed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003160_ELIDIBUS<tab>Elidibus... Ce nom me définit... et il guide chacun de mes actes<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que demandez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Why me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Comment ça, je vous définis<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Did you never consider other paths?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pourquoi ne pas vivre au gré de ses désirs, plutôt<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003170_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Why you? Why <var 1A 02 /var>not<var 1A 01 /var> you? Had I chosen another, we would never have made it this far. Or do I mistake your meaning...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003170_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ah... C'est-à-dire que... c'est difficile à expliquer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003180_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I did─but I chose not to walk them, thank the gods. Why ever would you ask me such a thing?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003180_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je ne me suis pas imposé ce choix, c'est simplement celui que j'ai fait. Quant à mes raisons... Difficile de répondre... Tiens-tu tant que ça à les connaître<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>...Elidibus spoke in similar terms, you say? How curious.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>D'accord... Elidibus t'a dit quelque chose de similaire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003200_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>To answer your question, then, I made my choice for reasons which seemed obvious to me, but may not to any other.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003200_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je ne saurais pas expliquer ses paroles à sa place. Quant aux miennes... Comment dire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003210_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>There were the expectations I placed upon myself before beginning my slumber. And the expectations of those who roused me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003210_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>“Tu seras la lueur qui me guidera à mon réveil...” Non seulement je t'avais dit ça avant que je ne m'enferme dans la Tour de Cristal, mais ceux qui me tirèrent de mon sommeil te considéraient comme leur exemple, eux aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Of course, I had the choice to turn my back on the lot of it. But in the end, it was no choice at all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>La véritable question serait plutôt... ce qui m'a poussé à tenir cette promesse...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I cherish the time I spent with you and the others. What I wouldn't give to return to those halcyon days...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>S'il y a bien un souvenir que je chéris plus que tout, c'est celui de cette époque où je vous ai accompagnés dans vos aventures.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Chasing ancient secrets, overcoming trial after trial with the aid of like-minded comrades...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Une bande d'amis bravant tous les dangers afin d'élucider un mystère millénaire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And what remarkable comrades they were. In such company, I felt as if I were a character in the epic tales that had stirred my heart as a boy. As if my dream had come true...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Et de véritables héros, en plus<var 1D /var>! Ceux des livres que je lisais dans mon enfance ne vous arrivaient pas à la cheville<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>It hadn't, of course, for I was no hero. Neither then nor after. Though the world to which I awakened, and the First were beset with myriad problems, I rarely knew how best to play my part.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Le monde que j'ai découvert à mon réveil et celui vers lequel j'ai voyagé après étaient tous deux en proie à un terrible destin. Plus d'une fois, j'ai douté du chemin à emprunter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>There was, however, one thing of which I was certain: that I could not bear to let those dear to me meet a tragic end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mais une certitude ne m'a jamais quitté, celle que votre histoire ne pouvait finir ainsi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I'm afraid our time is up. Go.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Fini la pause, on dirait... Je vais les ralentir. Toi, fonce<var 1D /var>! Et ne te retourne pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Rest assured you haven't seen the last of me. I wouldn't dream of playing my trump card save in your presence.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ne t'en fais pas pour moi, je te rejoindrai. J'abattrai alors ma carte maîtresse, et tu en resteras pantois. Je te le garantis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Break!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Fossile<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003310_ELIDIBUS<tab>Memories of a possible future...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003310_ELIDIBUS<tab>Les souvenirs d'un futur qui fut...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003320_ELIDIBUS<tab>Worthless, all. Worthless as memories of the only past. Fated to fray and fade into oblivion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003320_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hmpf... Un tissu d'affabulations au même titre que le passé. L'un comme l'autre est destiné à être corrompu et affadi par l'inconstance de notre esprit...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003330_ELIDIBUS<tab>Leaving naught but a gaping void...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003330_ELIDIBUS<tab>Étais-je le même autrefois...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003340_ELIDIBUS<tab>The Waking...Sands? ...Yes, that was the place. The place I first made myself known to you and yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003340_ELIDIBUS<tab>Nous nous sommes rencontrés pour la première fois dans votre “Refuge des sables”, si ma mémoire est bonne...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003350_ELIDIBUS<tab>The seventh Rejoining had left the realm listing dangerously towards Darkness. And events were unfolding that threatened to push it over the brink.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003350_ELIDIBUS<tab>Le septième fléau avait mis Éorzéa sens dessus dessous. Et les Ténèbres qui l'avaient causé menaçaient à nouveau de s'emballer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003360_ELIDIBUS<tab>Thus did I approach you, in my capacity as Emissary, thinking that you would make a useful pawn...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003360_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je t'ai donc approché<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, pensant faire de toi ma marionnette...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003370_ELIDIBUS<tab>But I was wrong, and for my misstep did Lahabrea and Emet-Selch pay the ultimate price. Leaving me the last of the unsundered.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003370_ELIDIBUS<tab>Mon manque de discernement nous a coûté Lahabrea et Emet-Selch...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003380_ELIDIBUS<tab>My remaining brethren, fragmented as they are, cannot hope to see our mission to its end. It falls to me alone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003380_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je suis désormais le dernier des Asciens originels... Le dernier capable de réaliser notre vœu de renaissance, car ce ne sont pas ces transmigrés qui y parviendront.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003390_ELIDIBUS<tab>Defeat is not an option. I will strike you down. I will resurrect Lord Zodiark. And I will bring back those who sacrificed themselves to call Him forth.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003390_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je vais te vaincre... restituer sa force à Zordiarche... et ramener à la vie tous ceux qui ont fait l'ultime sacrifice pour l'invoquer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003400_ELIDIBUS<tab>Though it take a thousand thousand years, upon my honor as Elidibus, Emissary of the Convocation of Fourteen, I will see this done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003400_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je remplirai mon office, que cela prenne des centaines ou des milliers d'années. Car je suis Elidibus, le médiateur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003410_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>But know that his devotion is not without reason. Even if he himself can no longer remember what that reason is.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003410_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Garde à l'esprit qu'il doit avoir une raison de faire tout cela, même si lui-même l'a oubliée depuis tout ce temps.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003420_LAHABREA<tab>(-Convocation Speaker-)<var 48 F20223 /var>You worry too much, Elidibus. This dedication to your duty verges on obsession.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003420_LAHABREA<tab>(-Président du Concile des Quatorze-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Quoique, non. Ton excès de zèle prouve surtout le respect que tu voues à ta fonction, Elidibus.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003430_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003430_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>（★未使用／削除予定★）

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Those who once relied upon you are no more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu n'as plus rien à médier, Elidibus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>However hard you struggle, you will never bring back the Convocation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Le Concile des Quatorze n'est plus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003440_ELIDIBUS<tab>What of it!? I have my mission!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003440_ELIDIBUS<tab>Quelle importance<var 1D /var>!? Peu importe que je sois seul ou non, du moment que notre plan se réalise<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003450_ELIDIBUS<tab>I am Elidibus! And it is my duty to steer mankind and the very star upon their true course. This I swore to...to someone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003450_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je suis Elidibus<var 1D /var>! Et j'œuvre pour le plus grand bien de la planète et de ses habitants<var 1D /var>! Car j'ai prêté serment<var 1D /var>! J'ai prêté le serment de... le serment...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003460_ELIDIBUS<tab>We spoke, and I swore...what? What did I...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003460_ELIDIBUS<tab>Le serment...<var 1D /var>? Lequel...<var 1D /var>? À qui l'avais-je prononcé...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003470_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003470_ELIDIBUS<tab>(Rire léger)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003480_ELIDIBUS<tab>This pain, this torment...is nothing! No more than must be suffered to deliver the world from its doom! No more than any of you malformed creatures have known!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003480_ELIDIBUS<tab>Cette douleur n'est rien<var 1D /var>! Vous le savez mieux que quiconque<var 1D /var>! Un monde ne peut être sauvé que dans la souffrance et dans la peine<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003490_ELIDIBUS<tab>Even should you lose all that is dear to you. Even should it cost you your life...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003490_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'ai perdu tout ce qui m'était cher, je suis même allé jusqu'à sacrifier ma propre vie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003500_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>Even should you lose all that is dear to you. Even should it cost you your life...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003500_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>J'ai perdu tout ce qui m'était cher, je suis même allé jusqu'à sacrifier ma propre vie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003510_ELIDIBUS<tab>You bear the burden and fight on, kicking and screaming until your last breath is spent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003510_ELIDIBUS<tab>Pourquoi devrais-je renoncer à accomplir mon devoir maintenant<var 1D /var>!? Alors que j'ai déjà tant donné<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003520_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>You bear the burden and fight on, kicking and screaming until your last breath is spent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003520_DUMMYARDBERT<tab>Pourquoi devrais-je renoncer à accomplir mon devoir maintenant<var 1D /var>!? Alors que j'ai déjà tant donné<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003530_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>(-Voice from Within-)Aye, it's true. We've lost much and more. Known unimaginable suffering.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003530_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>(-Voix résonnant au fond de votre âme-)Lui comme nous avons beaucoup sacrifié... Hmm... Oui... Oui c'est vrai...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003540_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>(-Voice from Within-)But through it all, we never, ever forgot what was dear to us. And that's what gave us the strength to carry on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003540_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>(-Voix résonnant au fond de votre âme-)Mais contrairement à lui, on est toujours allés de l'avant<var 1D /var>! Sans oublier ce qui compte vraiment<var 1D /var>! Seule une issue est possible.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Elidibus...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Elidibus...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>You've no fight left to fight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu n'as plus de raison de te battre... Plus de raison de vivre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A9_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I will put an end to this.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A9_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Mettons un terme à toute cette souffrance.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003550_ELIDIBUS<tab>No! NO! It will not end here!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003550_ELIDIBUS<tab>Jamais... Jamais je ne renoncerai<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003560_ELIDIBUS<tab>Champions from beyond the rift, heed my call! The time is come to deliver your brethren from darkness!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003560_ELIDIBUS<tab>Héros, répondez à mon appel<var 1D /var>! Traversez les dimensions<var 1D /var>! Brandissez vos armes et récriez-vous face à votre destin funeste<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003570_ELIDIBUS<tab>My heart's sole desire is a world free of sorrow. Join with me now in hope and prayer...for the salvation of all!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003570_ELIDIBUS<tab>Faites le vœu d'un monde sans souffrance et sans peine<var 1D /var>! Priez pour un avenir radieux<var 1D /var>! Ensemble, préservons ce qui nous est cher<var 1D /var>! Et sauvons tous ceux qui peuvent l'être<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003580_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-Elidibus-)If you would usher in the end, then with my all shall I oppose you...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003580_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-Elidibus-)Puisque tu sembles déterminé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à sonner notre glas, je me dresse une ultime fois contre toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003590_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-Elidibus-)...As the avatar of those mortal heroes who fought unfalteringly, in all their imperfection! As the Warrior of Light incarnate!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003590_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-Elidibus-)Au nom de tous ces succédanés<var 1D /var>! De tous ces héros misérables et imparfaits qui n'ont jamais abandonné le combat<var 1D /var>! Au nom des Guerriers de la Lumière<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003600_ELIDIBUS<tab>Come, Warrior of Darkness! Let us finish this!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003600_ELIDIBUS<tab>En garde<var 1D /var>! <var 08 E905 ((Défenseuse)) ((Défenseur)) /var> des Ténèbres<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003610_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003610_ELIDIBUS<tab>(surpris)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003620_EMETSELCH<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Herein I commit the chronicle of the traveler. Shepherd to the stars in the dark.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003620_EMETSELCH<tab>À toi, <var 08 E905 ((ma plus chère amie)) ((mon plus cher ami)) /var> qui n'a eu de cesse de rapprocher les pauvres étoiles déchues que nous sommes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003630_EMETSELCH<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Though the world be sundered and our souls set adrift, where you walk, my dearest friend, fate shall surely follow.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003630_EMETSELCH<tab>Même maintenant, alors que nous sommes plus que jamais séparés par le temps, l'espace et les sentiments, il te suffirait d'un geste, d'une parole, pour nous unir à nouveau.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003640_EMETSELCH<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>For yours is the Fourteenth seat─the seat of Azem.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003640_EMETSELCH<tab>Quatorzième, ici j'inscris ton nom<var 1D /var>: Azem.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003650_ELIDIBUS<tab>An invocation of eld...though not of Hydaelyn's making... What are you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003650_ELIDIBUS<tab>Qui es-tu...<var 1D /var>? Qui es-tu pour faire revivre la magie de l'ancien monde...<var 1D /var>? Et sans l'aide d'Hydaelyn, qui plus est<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003660_ELIDIBUS<tab>No─it matters not! You are the enemy, and you will fall! Even should it cost me everything, I will not forsake my duty!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003660_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hmpf... Quelle importance<var 1D /var>? Qui ou quoi que tu sois, tu vas mourir ici et maintenant<var 1D /var>! Devrais-je pour cela sacrifier tout ce qu'il me reste<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003670_ELIDIBUS<tab>Fool! You have achieved nothing! I am immortal, and I will never surrender!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003670_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ne crois pas un instant... que j'en ai fini avec toi... Je suis immortel...<var 1D /var>! Et je me battrai pour l'éternité s'il le faut<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003680_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003680_ELIDIBUS<tab>(stupeur, il est stoppé dans son élan)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003690_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Elidibus. So fixated were you on my memories of the future, you failed to heed the lessons of the past.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003690_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je te tiens<var 1D /var>! Hah<var 1D /var>! As-tu apprécié les souvenirs de mon futur<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003700_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Your obsession blinded you to the true nature of this tower─this beacon of hope for mankind.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003700_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, tu as oublié que cette Tour vient du passé. C'est un symbole d'espoir légué par nos ancêtres<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003710_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Created to serve as a reservoir for the limitless energy of the heavens! To harness and bind the boundless─not unlike white auracite!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003710_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Allag l'avait construite afin de recueillir l'énergie céleste. Tu te tiens sur la plus puissante auralithe blanche qui ait jamais brillé sur le monde<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003720_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Your ill-begotten power, obtained by exploiting that which is best in us... I shall have it, your soul and all!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003720_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ces pouvoirs que tu as acquis en manipulant les aspirations de notre peuple... de nos héros<var 1D /var>! Je t'en destitue<var 1D /var>! Et de ton âme avec<var 1D /var>!!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003730_ELIDIBUS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003730_ELIDIBUS<tab>(Hurlement de souffrance)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003740_ELIDIBUS<tab>This...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003740_ELIDIBUS<tab>Hmm<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003750_ELIDIBUS<tab>Yes... I would become Him. I would save everyone. This I believed. Yet still they cried out, in rage and despair...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003750_ELIDIBUS<tab>Oh, je me souviens, maintenant... Mes amis... je voulais les aider... leur apporter la salvation en devenant Zordiarche... Mais ça ne suffit pas à faire cesser leurs lamentations...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003760_ELIDIBUS<tab>Divided─over the fate of the star. A rare occurrence, always fleeting. But not this time. Not this time...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003760_ELIDIBUS<tab>Le Concile avait perdu sa cohésion... Face à l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, les avis divergeaient sur la marche à suivre pour sauver notre planète...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003770_ELIDIBUS<tab>Reconciliation. Elidibus. I was needed. I withdrew myself from Zodiark. For them...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003770_ELIDIBUS<tab>Ça ne leur ressemblait pas... Plus que jamais, ils avaient besoin d'Elidibus... Ils avaient besoin de moi... Alors, je me suis détaché de Zordiarche pour voler à leur secours...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003780_ELIDIBUS<tab>My people. My brothers. ...My friends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003780_ELIDIBUS<tab>C'est ça... Chacun d'eux, je les aimais plus que tout...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003790_ELIDIBUS<tab>Stay strong. Keep the faith. At duty's end, we will meet again. We will. We will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003790_ELIDIBUS<tab>J'espérais qu'en ac<var 16 /var>com<var 16 /var>plis<var 16 /var>sant mon devoir, je pourrais à nouveau les voir souriants et heureux...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003800_ELIDIBUS<tab>The rains have ceased, and we have been graced with another beautiful day. But you are not here to see it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003800_ELIDIBUS<tab>Je devais partir en dernier... Comment aurais-je pu abandonner mes amis, esseulés en ce bas monde<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003810_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I concede, I may have overexerted myself.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003810_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Désolé, j'y suis allé un peu trop fort, on dirait.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003820_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Steady now, and listen. I told you before that I had a plan, and that when all was said and done, I would ask a favor of you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003820_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous voilà enfin tranquilles. Nous allons pouvoir parler, maintenant que j'ai accompli... mon devoir d'exarque...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003830_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>We have averted the Eighth Umbral Calamity. Found a way for everyone to return to the Source, and...last but not least, we have secured the future of all the people of Norvrandt. We have won, my friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003830_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Le huitième fléau n'aura plus lieu... et nous avons trouvé le moyen de renvoyer tes amis dans leur monde. Quant aux habitants de Cristarium... l'avenir leur tend désormais les bras.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003840_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>So I hope you'll forgive me this moment of selfishness. And...while I wouldn't want you to feel obliged...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003840_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>L'heure est aux réjouissances, alors souris, et écoute ce que j'ai à te dire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003850_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Promise me you'll take me on your next adventure. A journey. Together. That's all I ask.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003850_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-G'raha Tia-)Je veux... Je veux voyager avec toi. Je veux vivre avec toi ta prochaine aventure, alors emmène-moi, s'il te plaît.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I promise.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je te le promets... Raha.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>You could've asked me earlier!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu aurais pu demander plus tôt<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003860_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003860_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(rire)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003870_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>If I were to tell you that this isn't the end─that we will meet again─would you believe me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003870_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-G'raha Tia-)On se reverra... Tu me fais confiance, maintenant, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003880_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Thank you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003880_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-G'raha Tia-)Merci.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>My friend. With you, my mind and memories shall travel to the ends of the world and beyond. But in this place shall my body stand immovable.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-G'raha Tia-)Ma mémoire et mon âme t'accompagneront. Quant à mon corps, il demeurera fièrement ici, dans cette Tour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>May it serve as an undying promise, not only to those who looked to me for leadership, but to any soul who has known despair, that hope is everlasting.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>(-G'raha Tia-)Ainsi, l'histoire de l'exarque du Cristal se poursuivra, et ce monde et son peuple auront toujours un guide pour les mener vers leur avenir radieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003910_RYNE<tab>There the Exarch would remain, keeping his silent vigil.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003910_RYNE<tab>On aurait dit que l'exarque assurait une veille éternelle, debout en haut de sa Tour...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003920_RYNE<tab>When the Scions were not released from his summoning spell, we proceeded with the plan to return them to the Source.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003920_RYNE<tab>Peut-être est-ce pour ça que les autres ne disparurent pas, et qu'ils durent se servir des conducteurs spirituels pour rentrer chez eux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003930_RYNE<tab>The Warrior of Darkness, however, retained <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> ability to traverse the two worlds at will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003930_RYNE<tab><var 08 E905 ((La Guerrière des Ténèbres)) ((Le Guerrier des Ténèbres)) /var>, quant à <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((lui)) /var>, put continuer librement ses allées et venues entre nos deux mondes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003940_RYNE<tab>And in time the Crystal Tower became a symbol of his link to the First─and of hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003940_RYNE<tab>La Tour de Cristal était devenue un phare, dont la lumière lui indiquerait toujours le chemin vers le premier reflet.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003950_RYNE<tab>And in time the Crystal Tower became a symbol of her link to the First─and of hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003950_RYNE<tab>La Tour de Cristal était devenue un phare, dont la lumière lui indiquerait toujours le chemin vers le premier reflet.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003960_DULIACHAI<tab>Oh... Oh, Alphinaud...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003960_DULIACHAI<tab>(sanglote)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003970_ALPHINAUD<tab>Please, Lady Chai, dry your eyes!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003970_ALPHINAUD<tab>Allons, Madame Chai... Reprenez-vous...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003980_DULIACHAI<tab>The thought of never seeing you again... It's more than my poor heart can bear!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003980_DULIACHAI<tab>Non... Non<var 1D /var>! Je rrrefuse de croire que ce soit nos adieux, mon cher Alphinaud. Ce n'est... pas possi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003990_DULIACHAI<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_003990_DULIACHAI<tab>(pleure à flots)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004000_CHAINUZZ<tab>Oh, it's you. As you can see, Alphinaud has broken the news.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004000_CHAINUZZ<tab>Ah, c'est vous<var 1D /var>! Comme vous pouvez le deviner, Alphinaud nous a tout expliqué.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004010_CHAINUZZ<tab>I don't know how to console her. She thinks we'll be lost without him.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004010_CHAINUZZ<tab>Elle rrreste in<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>so<var 16 /var>la<var 16 /var>ble depuis. Moi-même, je ne sais pas quoi faire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>You're certainly well loved.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Madame Chai était immensément attachée à vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Make sure you leave nothing unsaid.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Si vous avez quelque chose à dire, c'est le moment ou jamais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>A picture paints a thousand words!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A11_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Allons Maître, un peu de tenue<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004020_ALPHINAUD<tab>'Tis more than I deserve. Yet I am truly grateful, and will see that she knows as much.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004020_ALPHINAUD<tab>On me fait trop d'honneur... Je ne sais pas si j'aurai les mots justes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004030_ALPHINAUD<tab>Indeed, my friend. Nothing unsaid.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004030_ALPHINAUD<tab>Oui... Vous avez raison.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004040_ALPHINAUD<tab>You'll never let me forget it, will you. I'll have you know I completed the promised painting in the end. Be that as it may, there are times only words will suffice.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004040_ALPHINAUD<tab>Décidément, vous ne manquez jamais une occasion de vous payer ma tête<var 1D /var>! Je vous rappelle que j'ai terminé le portrait comme prévu<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004050_ALPHINAUD<tab>Lady Chai, I have a confession to make.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004050_ALPHINAUD<tab>Madame Chai, écoutez-moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004060_ALPHINAUD<tab>On the day we ousted Lord Vauthry, when I revealed the truth of his tyranny and your complicity in his crimes, I did so with great trepidation. Not out of fear that you wouldn't listen, but that you might never recover.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004060_ALPHINAUD<tab>Il y a longtemps, j'ai monté une or<var 16 /var>ga<var 16 /var>ni<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>tion afin de poursuivre mes idéaux et sauver le monde. Un excès de zèle pour lequel j'ai payé le prix fort...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004070_ALPHINAUD<tab>There was a time when I too, in my hubris, believed myself worthy to lord it over others. And when the lie was laid bare─when I was forced to confront the cost, the lives lost─it all but destroyed me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004070_ALPHINAUD<tab>Non... À vrai dire, je n'ai rien payé moi-même. J'ai semé le vent, et ce sont des personnes chères à mon cœur qui ont récolté la tempête. Une faute que je ne me pardonnerai jamais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004080_ALPHINAUD<tab>To awaken from a naive dream to so harsh a reality... I would have understood had you all surrendered to despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004080_ALPHINAUD<tab>Lorsque j'ai vu Vauthry, si enclin à poursuivre son rêve d'utopie sans aucun égard pour les autres... cela a ravivé ce souvenir. Je pense avoir reconnu en lui une certaine part de moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004090_ALPHINAUD<tab>But you didn't surrender. Far from it. You picked yourselves up and rose to the challenge.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004090_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est pour ça que... voir Eulmore prendre un nouveau départ m'a apporté beaucoup de joie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004100_ALPHINAUD<tab>You found a path forward and the strength to walk it─and to keep walking it─day after day.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004100_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ce que nous avons accompli ici n'atténue en rien mes erreurs, mais cette expérience m'a appris qu'il est toujours possible de se relever et de continuer à se battre pour ses idéaux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004110_ALPHINAUD<tab>But what struck me is how much faster you found it than I did.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004110_ALPHINAUD<tab>Cette ville a attisé la flamme du courage qui brûle en moi. Et grâce à elle, je continuerai à aller de l'avant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004120_CHAINUZZ<tab>...Really? It felt pretty slow to me! But rest assured, we'll make Eulmore into a nation anyone would be proud to call home...eventually.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004120_CHAINUZZ<tab>Bien dit. J'en ferai de même, en m'évertuant à fairrre d'Eulmore la plus accueillante de toutes les cités.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004130_CHAINUZZ<tab>You can still come and go as you please, I believe? When we have good tidings to report, I may trouble you to be their bearer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004130_CHAINUZZ<tab>Vous, en revanche, vous pourrez toujours nous rrrendre visite, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? Dans ce cas, je vous confierai une lettre de temps à autre pour tenir Alphinaud au courant de nos progrès.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004140_CHAINUZZ<tab>There may also be less-than-good tidings...in which event, I hope I can trouble you for your counsel.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004140_CHAINUZZ<tab>Enfin, il est possible que tout ne soit pas rrrose non plus... Auquel cas, vos conseils seront les bienvenus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004150_ALPHINAUD<tab>I should be honored to provide it, Master Chai.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004150_ALPHINAUD<tab>Avec plaisir<var 1D /var>! J'ai hâte de vous lire, Monsieur Chai.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004160_DULIACHAI<tab>Oh, Alphinaud... I know you aren't one to sit still, but do remember to take your ease from time to time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004160_DULIACHAI<tab>Ne faites pas de folies, d'accord<var 1D /var>? Peu importe que les mondes nous séparrrent, j'aurai chaque jour une pensée d'encouragement pour vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004170_DULIACHAI<tab>And no matter where you are, remember that there are people here who are praying for your health and happiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004170_DULIACHAI<tab>Nous tenons énormément à vous, ne l'oubliez jamais. Je vous souhaite une vie rrremplie de bonheur, Alphinaud.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004180_DULIACHAI<tab>Our brave and gentle artist. You have our love, now and always.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004180_DULIACHAI<tab>Oh... Mon brrrave et gentil petit peintre, comme vous allez me manquer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004190_ALPHINAUD<tab>And you mine. Please take care.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004190_ALPHINAUD<tab>Moi aussi, je vous souhaite tout le bonheur du monde, à tous les deux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004200_SETO<tab>Is that...Ardbert's crystal?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004200_SETO<tab>Ce cristal... Serait-ce celui d'Ardbert...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004210_SETO<tab>So it is. It has changed...but I would know it anywhere. However did you come by it?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004210_SETO<tab>J'en étais sûr. Il est différent, mais je le reconnais... Comment l'avez-vous donc obtenu<var 1D /var>? Je le croyais perdu depuis tout ce temps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004220_SETO<tab>...Then even in death, his enemies found a way to profit from his sacrifice. It grieves me to think of his body being used for evil ends...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004220_SETO<tab>Voilà donc ce qu'il advint de son corps... Quelle infamie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004230_SETO<tab>But thanks to you, his honor is restored, and he may finally find peace.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004230_SETO<tab>Je suis heureux que vous ayez préservé sa dignité. Grâce à vous, son honneur est sauf, tout comme celui de ses compagnons.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004240_SETO<tab>No words can express my gratitude. I will keep this crystal safe to the end of my days.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004240_SETO<tab>Merci beaucoup. Vous me faites avec ce cristal un cadeau inestimable, celui du souvenir d'un ami perdu. Je veillerai toujours sur lui.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004250_SETO<tab>Rest easy, my friend. You have earned it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004250_SETO<tab>Adieu, Ardbert... Puisses-tu cette fois trouver le repos que tu as toujours mérité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tell me, does anything strike you as different about my soul?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pouvez-vous toujours voir mon âme<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A12_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Close your eyes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A12_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Fermez les yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004260_SETO<tab>Your soul? Hm...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004260_SETO<tab>Votre âme<var 1D /var>? Hmm... Voyons voir...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004270_SETO<tab>Pardon? ...Hm! Very well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004270_SETO<tab>Fermer les yeux<var 1D /var>? Hmm... Si vous le désirez...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004280_SETO<tab>How can this be?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004280_SETO<tab>Je sens... comme une présence... si familière...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004290_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Seto, my old friend. You've grown!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004290_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Seto, vieille branche... Tu as drôlement grandi, dis donc<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004300_SETO<tab>Oh! Oh, Ardbert! How I've missed you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004300_SETO<tab>Ardbert<var 1D /var>! C'est toi, c'est vraiment toi<var 1D /var>! Cela faisait si longtemps que je rêvais de te revoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004310_SETO<tab>I'm sorry I couldn't keep you safe... Or even console you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004310_SETO<tab>Désolé de ne pas avoir été là pour te réconforter dans les moments difficiles... de ne pas avoir su te protéger lorsque tu avais besoin de moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004320_SETO<tab>Had I only learned to speak sooner, I would have told you how much you meant to me. How much I cared.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004320_SETO<tab>Si seulement j'avais réussi à parler plus tôt... J'aurais pu te dire tant de choses... à quel point je t'aime... et comme je souhaite que tu sois heureux....

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004330_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>I knew. I always knew.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004330_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Idiot... Tout ça, je le sais très bien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004340_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>But I'm happy to hear it nonetheless. Thank you, Seto. My partner in crime.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004340_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Merci pour tout... Je n'aurais pas pu rêver meilleur partenaire que toi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004350_SETO<tab>I see... His journey continues.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004350_SETO<tab>Je comprends... Son aventure n'est pas encore terminée. Et c'est avec vous qu'il la partage à présent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004360_SETO<tab>Then I will not yet bid him rest. With you, he may look forward to many more adventures.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004360_SETO<tab>J'ai été hâtif dans mes adieux. J'espère de tout cœur que vos tribulations vous permettront de voyager vers de nouvelles contrées tous les deux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004370_SETO<tab>It has been a while since last I flew. Perhaps I too will go on a little adventure. Ride the winds, seek the horizon... Yes. I think perhaps I will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004370_SETO<tab>Demain, j'irai battre des ailes pour la première fois depuis longtemps. Je sens les cieux qui m'appellent comme autrefois...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004380_RUNAR<tab>Master Matoya!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004380_RUNAR<tab>Matoya<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004390_RUNAR<tab>For too long, I have remained silent. But no longer. I could not bear it if you were to leave. Please stay! I beg of you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004390_RUNAR<tab>Matoya... Je ne veux pas croire que nous serons séparés à jamais. L'idée m'est in<var 16 /var>sup<var 16 /var>por<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>ble<var 1D /var>! Je vous en supplie, ne partez pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004400_YSHTOLA<tab>Runar... Please...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004400_YSHTOLA<tab>Runar...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004410_RUNAR<tab>...I jest. At least in part. Ahem. What I came to say is this...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004410_RUNAR<tab>Désolé. Je savais que ça vous mettrait dans l'embarras, mais je tenais à vous le dire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004420_RUNAR<tab>Thank you. Without your wisdom, your strength, and your kindness to guide us, our people would still be lost.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004420_RUNAR<tab>Matoya, votre arrivée fut une véritable bénédiction pour le peuple de la Nuit. C'est grâce à votre courage, votre présence d'esprit et votre bienveillance que chacun de nous a pu réapprendre à vivre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004430_RUNAR<tab>We will never forget you, Master Matoya. Wherever your journeys may take you, you will always be in our hearts.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004430_RUNAR<tab>Votre nom restera à jamais dans nos cœurs. Je vous souhaite de vivre heureuse, où que vous alliez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004435_YSHTOLA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004435_YSHTOLA<tab>(soupire)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004440_YSHTOLA<tab>And you in mine.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004440_YSHTOLA<tab>Moi aussi, je vous le souhaite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004450_YSHTOLA<tab>Remember that your people's journey─that <var 1A 02 /var>our<var 1A 01 /var> people's journey is yet ongoing. Your lives will change, and so too will your dreams. Yet come what may, you need not forsake your time-honored traditions, nor less your beliefs.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004450_YSHTOLA<tab>Les prières du peuple de la Nuit portent la sagesse que vous avez héritée de vos ancêtres. Elles évolueront sûrement comme l'a fait le monde, mais chérissez-les toujours.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004460_YSHTOLA<tab>But neither should you be beholden to them. For it was with curiosity and courage that the Night's Blessed first triumphed over adversity. New knowledge and new wisdom are ever worthy of pursuit.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004460_YSHTOLA<tab>Et n'oubliez pas que c'est en prenant soin les uns des autres que vous avez su surmonter les plus grands obstacles. Restez unis, c'est ce qui fera votre force.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004470_RUNAR<tab>Indeed they are. And so, until we return to the sunless sea, we shall endeavor to live our lives to the fullest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004470_RUNAR<tab>Je compte bien faire tout mon possible pour maintenir l'harmonie de notre peuple, jusqu'au jour où mon âme prendra son envol pour la sombre mer céleste.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004480_YSHTOLA<tab>That is well. But however great your strides, there may yet come a day when the challenges you face cannot be surmounted alone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004480_YSHTOLA<tab>Très bien... Mais il est des problèmes que toute la force et la sagesse du monde ne sauraient résoudre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004490_YSHTOLA<tab>On such a day...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004490_YSHTOLA<tab>Si vous deviez y faire face, eh bien...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004500_RUNAR<tab>On such a day?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004500_RUNAR<tab>Que devrons-nous faire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004505_YSHTOLA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004505_YSHTOLA<tab>Hé hé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004510_YSHTOLA<tab>You may call on me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004510_YSHTOLA<tab>Dans ce cas-là, une seule solution<var 1D /var>! Il faudra faire appel à moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004520_YSHTOLA<tab>Since a means to travel between worlds exists, you can be sure I will find a way to employ it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004520_YSHTOLA<tab>Je suis la grande Matoya<var 1D /var>! Je finirai bien par trouver un sort me permettant de voyager librement entre les mondes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004530_YSHTOLA<tab>And there remain so many mysteries here that want for solving.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004530_YSHTOLA<tab>Cet endroit ne m'a pas encore livré tous ses secrets, et je compte bien revenir pour les percer jusqu'au dernier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004540_RUNAR<tab>Master Matoya!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004540_RUNAR<tab>Oh, Matoya<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004550_YSHTOLA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004550_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais... E-enfin<var 1D /var>! Repose-moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004560_ALISAIE<tab>That's everyone, then. We've all said what we needed to.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004560_ALISAIE<tab>Nous voilà au complet<var 1D /var>! Je pense que nous avons tous pu faire nos adieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004570_URIANGER<tab>Even as we speak, Beq Lugg undertaketh their final inspection of our spirit vessels.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004570_URIANGER<tab>Beq Lugg procède aux derniers préparatifs des conducteurs spirituels.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004580_URIANGER<tab>When thine own preparations for the journey are complete, thou art to present thyself in the Ocular.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004580_URIANGER<tab>Il nous a demandé de le rejoindre dans la Tour quand nous serons tous prêts à partir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004590_RYNE<tab>Um...everyone?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004590_RYNE<tab>A-attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004600_RYNE<tab>I want to thank you all. On behalf of the First.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004600_RYNE<tab>Je... Je voulais vous remercier pour tout ce que vous avez fait pour nous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004610_RYNE<tab>You, and Minfilia, and the Exarch.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004610_RYNE<tab>Minfilia qui nous a sauvés du Déluge, l'exarque qui nous a redonné espoir, et enfin vous tous, les Guerriers des Ténèbres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004620_RYNE<tab>Without each and every one of you guiding us, fighting for us...we wouldn't be standing here now. There wouldn't even <var 1A 02 /var>be<var 1A 01 /var> a here. And no words can express our gratitude.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004620_RYNE<tab>Sans vous, Norvrandt n'existerait plus. Les mots ne suffisent pas à exprimer toute ma gratitude.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004630_RYNE<tab>We still have a lot to do, countless trials to overcome─but if it ever seems too much, I'll think of our time together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004630_RYNE<tab>Même si notre monde va mieux, l'avenir nous réserve encore sûrement quelques embûches. Dans ces moments-là, je penserai à vous et à nos aventures...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004640_RYNE<tab>The happy moments...and the sad─I will remember it all. And it will give me the strength to carry on without you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004640_RYNE<tab>Nos réussites, nos surprises et même quand le désespoir semblait inéluctable... Toutes ces expériences me permettront de franchir n'importe quel obstacle, j'en suis certaine.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004650_RYNE<tab>Because you made me who I am. Minfilia. Ryne.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004650_RYNE<tab>Je suis heureuse d'avoir été Minfilia... Et je suis heureuse d'être Ryne<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004660_RYNE<tab>To honor these names and these memories, I will stand with all the people of this land, and strive for a better tomorrow.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004660_RYNE<tab>Je continuerai à faire honneur à son nom et ferai tout pour offrir un avenir radieux aux gens de ce monde<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004670_URIANGER<tab>Thancred. I believe the honor of responding should rightfully be thine.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004670_URIANGER<tab>Thancred... Je pense que c'est à vous de répondre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004680_THANCRED<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004680_THANCRED<tab>(bref soupir)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004690_THANCRED<tab>I know better than most how much you've grown, and I have every confidence you'll make your people proud.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004690_THANCRED<tab>Même sans ton joli discours, je savais que tout irait bien pour toi. Je vois bien à quel point nos aventures t'ont fait mûrir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004700_THANCRED<tab>Gods know, I'm proud of you. I always will be. You deserve all the happiness in the world and more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004700_THANCRED<tab>Que je me trouve ici avec toi, ou aux confins d'un autre monde... sache que je ne souhaiterai jamais rien d'autre que ton bonheur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004710_RYNE<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004710_RYNE<tab>(inspiration, souffle court)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004720_LYNA<tab>(-???-)Might we also say a few words?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004720_LYNA<tab>(-???-)Nous aimerions vous dire un mot, nous aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Why, this is...just about all of you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Vous êtes tous là...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004740_LYNA<tab>To see you off seemed the least we could do.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004740_LYNA<tab>J'ai bien peur que rien ne puisse suffire à exprimer notre recon<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce. Laissez-nous donc au moins vous offrir des adieux dignes de ce nom.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004750_LYNA<tab>You risked your all for us─fought for a realm not your own. Before you came, we had never known the beauty of the night sky.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004750_LYNA<tab>Vous nous avez prouvé à maintes reprises votre valeur au combat. Vous avez risqué vos vies pour restaurer cette nuit que nous pensions perdue.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004760_LYNA<tab>Or the joy of your company.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004760_LYNA<tab>Mais surtout, vous avez été pour beaucoup d'entre nous bien plus que de simples compagnons d'armes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004770_LYNA<tab>Though it saddens us deeply to bid you farewell, it has ever been our way to send off friends with a smile.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004770_LYNA<tab>Bien sûr, nous sommes tristes de vous voir partir, mais la force de Cristarium est de savoir aller de l'avant, envers et contre tout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004780_LYNA<tab>Wherever your road should lead, we shall pray for your safety. And following your brave example, we shall continue to fight for the Crystarium.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004780_LYNA<tab>C'est pour cela que nous nous sommes réunis, pour vous offrir nos adieux chargés d'espoir pour l'avenir et vous souhaiter le meilleur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004790_ALISAIE<tab>With or without us, you've always taken good care of this city. I don't doubt for a moment you'll continue to do so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004790_ALISAIE<tab>Pas besoin de discours grandiloquent, nous savons que cette cité est entre de bonnes mains<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Aye, a more resilient people we have never known.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Oui... Cristarium est aussi solide que le lien qui vous unit. Et puis...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004810_ALPHINAUD<tab>As resilient and enduring as the tower that watches over you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Le symbole de l'espoir continue de briller en son centre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004820_LYNA<tab>To the last, we did not question the Exarch about his past. It is only now, when he can no longer tell us, that we believe we know the answer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004820_LYNA<tab>Au final, je n'aurai jamais demandé à l'exarque qui il était ou d'où il venait... Mais ses actes m'ont offert une réponse encore plus satisfaisante...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004830_LYNA<tab>We have heard what became of him, and what is about to be attempted.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004830_LYNA<tab>On m'a parlé de ce qui est arrivé à son corps, et... de ce qu'il pourrait encore advenir...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004840_LYNA<tab>All will be well, of this we are certain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004840_LYNA<tab>Je suis certaine que tout ira bien... J'en suis convaincue.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004850_LYNA<tab>How could it be otherwise, when every soul in the Crystarium is praying for it with all their heart?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004850_LYNA<tab>D'ailleurs, tous les Cristariens sont du même avis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004860_LYNA<tab>And so, when our lord awakens, I bid you give him a message.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004860_LYNA<tab>Quand il se réveillera... s'il se souvient encore de nous, faites-lui parvenir ce message, s'il vous plaît.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004870_LYNA<tab>Tell him he needn't worry about us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004870_LYNA<tab>“Ne vous en faites pas pour nous.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004880_LYNA<tab>That he need no longer hide who he truly is. That he should live his own life to the fullest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004880_LYNA<tab>“Ne vous cachez plus derrière vos petits secrets et vivez enfin votre vie comme vous l'entendez... Comme vous nous avez permis de le faire ici.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004890_LYNA<tab>And that if he should ever find himself reminiscing on the past with a smile, we shall be smiling with him.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004890_LYNA<tab>“Rappelez-vous tous les bons moments que nous avons passés ensemble, et sachez que vous serez pour toujours dans nos cœurs.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004900_LYNA<tab>Will you tell him this?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004900_LYNA<tab>Je peux compter sur vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Word for word.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je n'y manquerai pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A13_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll do my best.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A13_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Si tout se passe bien...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004910_LYNA<tab>Thank you. Please look after him for us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004910_LYNA<tab>Merci... Je vous confie notre exarque, celui qui nous a pendant si longtemps guidés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004920_LYNA<tab>I am sure you will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004920_LYNA<tab>Je suis certaine que vous y arriverez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004930_YSHTOLA<tab>I daresay we have all the good wishes we can carry. Let us be on our way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004930_YSHTOLA<tab>Je pense que nous en avons terminé avec nos adieux, il est temps de partir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004940_BEQLUGG<tab>All right, then. Pray proceed as instructed, beginning with your memories.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004940_BEQLUGG<tab>Bien... Il ne vous reste plus qu'à faire comme je vous l'ai montré. Commençons par vos souvenirs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004950_URIANGER<tab>The first step is complete. And all appeareth to be in order.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004950_URIANGER<tab>Cela semble avoir fonctionné.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004960_ALISAIE<tab>Well, that just leaves our souls, then.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004960_ALISAIE<tab>La prochaine étape, c'est d'y injecter nos âmes...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004970_ALISAIE<tab>We're in your hands, Angelo.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004970_ALISAIE<tab>Angelo, on compte sur toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004980_BEQLUGG<tab>It is done! The vessels have received of both their memories and their souls!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004980_BEQLUGG<tab>Ils ont réussi<var 1D /var>! Leurs mémoires et leurs âmes sont bien contenues dans les conducteurs spirituels<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004990_BEQLUGG<tab>I hereby entrust them to your care. They belong to you now. Just be sure to guard them well, yes?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_004990_BEQLUGG<tab>Bien, ces objets sont désormais vos possessions. Prenez-les, et faites attention à ne pas les faire tomber<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005000_RYNE<tab>This <var 1A 02 /var>will<var 1A 01 /var> work, won't it?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005000_RYNE<tab>Tout ira bien... N'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005010_BEQLUGG<tab>Our theories have held thus far.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005010_BEQLUGG<tab>Je le crois... Mais quand il s'agit de voyager entre les mondes, mes con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces sont plus que limitées...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005020_BEQLUGG<tab>But I make no promises about what is to come. Even the greatest mages in history knew better than to transport a soul across the rift. We, my dear, are in unknown territory.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005020_BEQLUGG<tab>Par conséquent, je ne peux pas dire avec certitude que leurs âmes supporteront le voyage.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005030_BEQLUGG<tab>Prepare as we might, we cannot account for all possibilities, and it is in such circumstances that accidents are wont to occur...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005030_BEQLUGG<tab>J'ai beau être spécialiste de la magie, j'en ignore encore beaucoup sur le fonc<var 16 /var>tion<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment de l'âme. Malgré tous ces préparatifs, un accident peut vite arriver... Mais il en va de même pour les miracles<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005040_BEQLUGG<tab>Yet miracles do happen. So let us pray, and will our friends home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005040_BEQLUGG<tab>Il ne nous reste plus qu'à prier. Quand on ne peut plus rien faire d'autre, nos pensées peuvent au moins être porteuses d'espoir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005050_RYNE<tab>I won't stop praying until I know they're safe.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005050_RYNE<tab>Vous avez raison... Je vais aussi prier pour que leur retour se passe sans encombre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005060_BEQLUGG<tab>All safely stowed away? I do hope so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005060_BEQLUGG<tab>Bien, je vois que vous les avez tous récupérés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005070_BEQLUGG<tab>All that remains, then, is to step into the mirror. Go now...and safe travels.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005070_BEQLUGG<tab>À présent, il ne vous reste plus qu'à traverser le portail qui mène à votre monde. Et... ne vous inquiétez pas, il restera toujours actif.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005080_ALISAIE<tab>Did it...? Are we...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005080_ALISAIE<tab>Ah... Je...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005090_THANCRED<tab>...We're home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005090_THANCRED<tab>Nous sommes enfin revenus...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005100_TATARU<tab>Oh! Oh, you're back! You're back! You're all back!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005100_TATARU<tab>Aaah<var 1D /var>! Les amis<var 1D /var>! Quel plaisir de vous voir enfin réveillés<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005110_YSHTOLA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005110_YSHTOLA<tab>(Pfffou)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005120_YSHTOLA<tab>Thank you. My body feels like a sack of popotoes, but otherwise I have never felt better.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005120_YSHTOLA<tab>Merci... Je me sens encore tout engourdie et j'ai la tête dans le coton, mais... tout a l'air d'aller.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005130_YSHTOLA<tab>That said, I doubt any of us will be fit to travel for some while. May we leave the rest to you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005130_YSHTOLA<tab>Il nous reste un dernier détail à régler, mais je ne pense pas être encore capable de bouger. On peut compter sur toi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005140_URIANGER<tab>The vessel beareth our comrade's blood. With it in thy possession, the way will surely open before thee.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005140_URIANGER<tab>Le dernier conducteur spirituel contient son sang. Vous devriez donc être en mesure d'ouvrir le sceau de la Tour, désormais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005150_TATARU<tab>What!? But you've only just got here!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005150_TATARU<tab>Hein<var 1D /var>!? Mais où va-t-<var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005160_ALPHINAUD<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005160_ALPHINAUD<tab>(petit rire complice)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005170_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tataru, might I trouble you to brew us all a pot of your special tea?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005170_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tataru, si ça ne te dérange pas, tu veux bien nous préparer quelques tasses de ton thé spécial<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005180_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ah! And we may require an extra cup.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005180_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ah, et prévois-en une de plus, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Yours is a long road, my friend, and it stretches on to places beyond imagining.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ainsi ton périple reprit, après ce bien long détour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005200_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>With your every step, these grand adventures shall grow more distant and faint.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005200_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Chaque pas en avant t'éloignant inexorablement un peu plus de tes aventures passées.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005210_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And there may come a day when you forget the faces and voices of those you have met along the way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005210_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Si un jour, tu venais à oublier toutes ces voix et tous ces visages croisés lors de ton épopée,

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>On that day, I bid you remember this...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>je voudrais que tu gardes au moins ceci dans un coin de ta mémoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>That no matter how far your journey may take you, you stand where you stand by virtue of the road you walked to get there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Quel que soit le temps qui passe, où que tu ailles, ces aventures feront toujours partie de toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>For in times of hardship, when you fear you cannot go on...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Et n'oublie pas, peu importe les défis que tu auras à surmonter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>The joy you have known, the pain you have felt, the prayers you have whispered and answered─they shall ever be your strength and your comfort.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tu ne seras jamais vraiment seul<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>... Car tous ces moments de joie, et de tristesse... ainsi que tous ces espoirs t'ac<var 16 /var>com<var 16 /var>pa<var 16 /var>gnent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>This I hope─I believe, here at memory's end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Voilà le dernier souvenir que je voulais te léguer, et avec lui, mon dernier souhait.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005270_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Some days later...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005270_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Quelques jours plus tard...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005280_ALISAIE<tab>[LOW, ANNOYED SIGH]
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005280_ALISAIE<tab>(grand soupir)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005290_ALPHINAUD<tab>What is it, Alisaie? Are you all right? Do you still feel under the weather?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005290_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu ne te sens pas bien, Alisaie<var 1D /var>? Tu n'es pas encore entièrement remise...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005300_ALISAIE<tab>Physically, I couldn't be better. Thanks to Krile's ministrations, I'm already looking forward to our next fight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005300_ALISAIE<tab>Si si, ça va... Grâce aux soins de Krile, je ne me sens même pas affaiblie par ces semaines de coma.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005310_ALISAIE<tab>But seriously─don't you have anything to say about <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var>?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005310_ALISAIE<tab>Mais dis-moi, ça te fait rien à toi de les voir comme ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005320_YSHTOLA<tab>No less impressive than our garments. You've outdone yourself, Tataru.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005320_YSHTOLA<tab>La tenue est exactement identique<var 1D /var>! Et ce bâton... une vraie merveille.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005330_TATARU<tab>To give credit where it's due, I had help from a certain fiery pixie who visited me in my dreams. They gave me all the information I needed to get the details just right.
