target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005330_TATARU<tab>Hé hé hé<var 1D /var>! Ça, vous le devez à cette gentille fée qui apparaît dans mes rêves<var 1D /var>! C'est elle qui m'a décrit vos tenues du premier reflet dans les moindres détails<var 1D /var>! Il ne me restait plus qu'à faire parler mes talents de couturière<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005340_TATARU<tab>For your weapons, though, I needed a <var 1A 02 /var>lot<var 1A 01 /var> more help... Thankfully, our favorite heads of state were happy to place their finest craftsmen at my exclusive disposal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005340_TATARU<tab>Pour vos armes, en revanche, j'ai dû demander de l'aide à droite et à gauche. Heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, les re<var 16 /var>pré<var 16 /var>sen<var 16 /var>tants de l'Alliance éorzéenne se sont montrés très accommodants.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005350_TATARU<tab>Oh, and speaking of the Alliance leaders, they all express their “unreserved elation at your safe return,” and promise to come and see you in person as soon as they can.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005350_TATARU<tab>Ah, et d'ailleurs, ils s'excusent de ne pas pouvoir venir vous saluer dans l'immédiat, et vous font savoir qu'ils sont ravis de votre retour<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005360_THANCRED<tab>They really needn't have gone to such trouble─but we'll be keeping these gifts all the same. Do pass on our gratitude.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005360_THANCRED<tab>Eh bien... C'est qu'on est gâtés, dites donc... Je compte sur toi pour leur transmettre nos re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ments.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005370_ALISAIE<tab>I realize we haven't taken up new martial arts, nor have I ever been one to set much store by appearances...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005370_ALISAIE<tab>Toi et moi, on n'a pas changé de style de combat, et puis... Je suis attachée à cette tenue, mais...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005380_ALISAIE<tab>But I can't help feeling a certain lack of...I don't know, personal development.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005380_ALISAIE<tab>Aaah<var 1D /var>! J'ai l'impression qu'on fait du sur place<var 1D /var>! C'est pas juste<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005390_ALPHINAUD<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005390_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ha ha...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005400_ALPHINAUD<tab>I quite understand. But as you observed, the others had the more pressing need. Rest assured, our turn will come.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005400_ALPHINAUD<tab>Allons, allons. Ils en avaient plus besoin que nous. Toi et moi, nous avons déjà beaucoup appris pendant ce séjour en Norvrandt, tu ne crois pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005410_KRILE<tab>If I expend any more aether, I swear I will blink out of existence. I need a bite to eat.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005410_KRILE<tab>(long soupir)... Ce n'était pas de tout repos... J'ai l'estomac dans les talons après tous ces efforts, moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005420_KRILE<tab>Tataru, a cup of tea, if you would be so kind. And something sweet.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005420_KRILE<tab>Tataru, je prendrais bien une tasse de thé aussi... Et quelque chose à grignoter, si possible.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005430_URIANGER<tab>By Mistress Krile's exhausted state, may I assume that the ward hath been restored?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005430_URIANGER<tab>Krile semble ter<var 16 /var>ri<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment épuisée... j'en déduis que la barrière magique est à nouveau en place<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005440_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)Indeed. We succeeded in weaving it anew, albeit at a slightly diminished potency than when I had Beq Lugg's assistance.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005440_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)Oui. J'ai demandé à Krile de m'aider comme Beq Lugg l'avait fait. On a rrréussi tant bien que mal.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005450_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)It is no cause for concern, though. The tower is not easily reached, never mind breached. And even should some few succeed, their presence won't escape my notice.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005450_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)Elle n'est pas aussi puissante, mais elle devrait au moins tenirrr la majorité des monstres éloignés de la Tour. Et si quelque chose réussit à la traverser, je le saurai im<var 16 /var>mé<var 16 /var>dia<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005460_URIANGER<tab>Excellent. Said duty thus discharged, thou art free to go wheresoever thy fancy taketh thee.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005460_URIANGER<tab>Excellente nouvelle. Vous êtes donc libre d'aller où bon vous semble à présent, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005470_URIANGER<tab>Upon which note─hast thou perchance come to a decision? The offer remaineth open.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005470_URIANGER<tab>Avez-vous réfléchi à notre proposition de l'autre jour<var 1D /var>? Nous attendons toujours votre réponse...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005480_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)Well...if you're certain that's what you... I-I mean, if you think I...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005480_GRAHATIA<tab>(-???-)Euh... E-eh bien... Ce serait avec plaisirrr... Si ça ne vous dérange pas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_Q14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que faites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Ne rien dire

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A14_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>G'raha, really.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_A14_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>L'appeler par son nom

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005490_GRAHATIA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005490_GRAHATIA<tab>Euh...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005500_GRAHATIA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005500_GRAHATIA<tab>(surpris)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005510_GRAHATIA<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005510_GRAHATIA<tab>Aah... Bon<var 1D /var>! Il faut bien se lancer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005520_GRAHATIA<tab>I accept. Henceforth, I shall count myself a Scion of the Seventh Dawn.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005520_GRAHATIA<tab>Moi, G'raha Tia, accepte de rrrejoindre les Héritiers de la Septième Aube<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005530_GRAHATIA<tab>G'raha Tia, at your service.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005530_GRAHATIA<tab>Merci de m'accueillir parrrmi vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005540_GRAHATIA<tab>When I was a boy, many long years ago, I yearned to stand tall as the heroes of eld.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005540_GRAHATIA<tab>Il m'arrive parfois de repenser à ma tendrrre enfance... Je me passionnais pour ces héros qui peuplent les livres et les chansons.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005550_UNSETTLEDRESEARCHER<tab>Help! Somebody help!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005550_UNSETTLEDRESEARCHER<tab>A-au secours<var 1D /var>!!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005560_UNSETTLEDRESEARCHER<tab>Hippogryphs! Hippogryphs on the rampage! A giant flock of 'em! Please, we need help!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005560_UNSETTLEDRESEARCHER<tab>Une meute d'hippogriffes nous a attaqués pas loin d'ici<var 1D /var>! Il nous faut de l'aide, je vous en prie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005570_ALISAIE<tab>I could do with a little rampage myself.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005570_ALISAIE<tab>Voilà l'occasion parfaite pour se remettre en jambe<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005580_ALPHINAUD<tab>What!? Now wait just a─
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005580_ALPHINAUD<tab>Hé oh, Alisaie<var 1D /var>! Attends<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005590_ALPHINAUD<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005590_ALPHINAUD<tab>(soupire)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005600_GRAHATIA<tab>But like a fool seeking to pluck the stars from the heavens, my every attempt to reprise their deeds fell short...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005600_GRAHATIA<tab>C'était comme s'ils vivaient dans un autre monde, horrrs d'atteinte. Je pouvais les imiter, mais... ça n'allait pas plus loin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005610_YSHTOLA<tab>I will join the fray when I've finished my tea.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005610_YSHTOLA<tab>Je vais les rejoindre. Après avoir fini mon thé, évidemment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005620_URIANGER<tab>Thus did the avatar of destruction descend, and in her wake leave naught but tears and ash...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005620_URIANGER<tab>Oh... Par les Douze... Je peux déjà sentir la terre calcinée...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005630_GRAHATIA<tab>And then, one day, an all but forgotten dream from my youth stood before me, in the flesh.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005630_GRAHATIA<tab>Je ne me doutais pas qu'un beau jourrr, l'incarnation de tous mes rêves se tiendrait devant moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005640_GRAHATIA<tab>So it was that a new adventure began...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005640_GRAHATIA<tab>Pourrr nous tous, une nouvelle aventure commençait.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005650_ZENOS<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005650_ZENOS<tab>(souffle)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005660_ZENOS<tab>The memory of a dying world's end, night after night... And I thought it but a tired old dream.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005660_ZENOS<tab>Ah... L'apocalypse... Ces visions égayent agré<var 16 /var>a<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment mes rêves d'habitude si insipides...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005670_FANDANIEL<tab>I say... I knew that securing the palace would provide Your Radiance with depressingly little sport─but that you should fall asleep out of boredom!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005670_FANDANIEL<tab>Tiens tiens tiens<var 1D /var>! Je savais que ce serait un jeu d'enfant pour vous de prendre le contrôle du château, mais de là à piquer un somme sur le trône<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005680_FANDANIEL<tab>Splendid! Truly splendid! And my own preparations, you will be pleased to hear, proceed apace.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005680_FANDANIEL<tab>Excellent<var 1D /var>! Vraiment excellent<var 1D /var>! Grâce à vous, tout commence à se mettre en place comme je l'espérais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005690_FANDANIEL<tab>Oh yes, they proceed very well indeed. Frighteningly so. And we owe it not least of all to this singularly useful body I chanced to find.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005690_FANDANIEL<tab>Tout se déroule si bien que c'en serait presque effrayant. Force est de constater que j'ai fait un excellent in<var 16 /var>ves<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment en choisissant ce corps comme nouveau pantin, ha ha ha...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005700_FANDANIEL<tab>With the Populares now all but destroyed, it will be the simplest of tasks to discredit their groundless assertions that I met with a grisly end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005700_FANDANIEL<tab>Les quelques Populares pouvant attester de ma “mort” ont été exterminés. Et dans le pire des cas, j'ai quelques excuses dans mon sac pour justifier ma survie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005710_FANDANIEL<tab>And as the very-much-alive lord of House Brutus, I have a vast fortune at my disposal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005710_FANDANIEL<tab>Et que dire de la maison Brutus<var 1D /var>! Si ce n'est que sa fortune dépasse tout ce que j'espérais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005720_FANDANIEL<tab>Ahhh, money, money, money! The great motivator! There is simply no better way to move men─and expedite plans─than with its alluring glint, would you not agree?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005720_FANDANIEL<tab>Vous entendez ce bruit<var 1D /var>!? Celui de l'argent sonnant et trébuchant<var 1D /var>! Aaaah, quelle délicieuse mélodie<var 1D /var>! Voilà qui devrait grandement aider notre plan<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005730_FANDANIEL<tab>But wait...! Were we not acquainted, you and...“I”?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005730_FANDANIEL<tab>Oh, pardonnez-moi... J'oubliais que vous avez déjà eu affaire à “moi”....

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005740_FANDANIEL<tab>(-White-robed Figure-)Should our familiarity cause you distress, I beg your forgiveness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005740_FANDANIEL<tab>(-Homme à la robe blanche-)Mes petits jeux ont-ils terni votre humeur, Votre Altesse<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005750_ZENOS<tab>...What did you say your name was?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005750_ZENOS<tab>Ce visage ne me dit rien...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005760_FANDANIEL<tab>(-White-robed Figure-)Ahhh, a dagger through my heart! That my deepest desire should forever remain unfulfilled! To live unrecognized! To die forgotten!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005760_FANDANIEL<tab>(-Homme à la robe blanche-)Aah<var 1D /var>! Vous me chagrinez<var 1D /var>! Pourtant, les souvenirs de ma “vie” précédente semblent indiquer tout le contraire<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005770_FANDANIEL<tab>(-White-robed Figure-)So it goes. Whatever this flesh may have been before, it serves only as a vessel now.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005770_FANDANIEL<tab>(-Homme à la robe blanche-)Pauvre de lui... Ainsi va la vie<var 1D /var>! Si cette enveloppe ne vous sied guère, Votre Altesse, je peux toujours en changer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005780_FANDANIEL<tab>And I, faithful Fandaniel, labor only to advance my lord's ambitions.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005780_FANDANIEL<tab>(-Homme à la robe blanche-)N'oubliez pas qu'il s'agit de moi, Fandaniel, à l'intérieur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005790_FANDANIEL<tab>Speaking of which, with the palace in our hands, we may now proceed with the next phase of the plan.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005790_FANDANIEL<tab>Bien bien, bien... Maintenant que le château est à nous, il est temps de passer à la suite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005800_FANDANIEL<tab>But how very odd... Despite all our havoc wreaking, old Elidibus did not deign to appear. Dare I hope...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005800_FANDANIEL<tab>Mais j'y pense... Elidibus n'est pas intervenu malgré tout le chaos que nous avons déchaîné...<var 1D /var>? Aurait-il finalement passé l'arme à gauche<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005810_FANDANIEL<tab>That the last of the unsundered...is gone?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005810_FANDANIEL<tab>Cela marquerait la fin des Asciens originels<var 1D /var>! Vous vous rendez compte<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005820_FANDANIEL<tab>No subtitles. Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005820_FANDANIEL<tab>(rire maniaque)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005830_FANDANIEL<tab>Imagine it! Bound no more by the shackles of moldering memories─of damnable duty! Free at last to live for the moment!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005830_FANDANIEL<tab>C'est absolument parfait<var 1D /var>! Plus besoin de suivre leurs lubies de restaurer l'ancien monde<var 1D /var>! Nous allons enfin pouvoir vivre dans le présent et faire de lui ce qu'il nous plaît<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005840_FANDANIEL<tab>Your Radiance. But give the word, and I shall go forth and prepare for you your hunting ground.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005840_FANDANIEL<tab>Dites, Votre Altesse... N'est-il pas enfin temps de vous bâtir un terrain de chasse personnel, comme vous l'avez toujours souhaité<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005850_GRAHATIA<tab>That which awaited was a fell beast.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005850_GRAHATIA<tab>Ce qui attendait notre <var 08 E905 ((hérrroïne)) ((hérrros)) /var> n'était pas un homme...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005860_GRAHATIA<tab>Ferocious. Ravenous. Remorseless.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005860_GRAHATIA<tab>Mais la plus sinistrrre... et la plus dangereuse des bêtes san<var 16 /var>gui<var 16 /var>nai<var 16 /var>res.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005870_ZENOS<tab>...Do as you will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005870_ZENOS<tab>Fais comme tu l'entends...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005880_ZENOS<tab>It has been too, too long, my friend...and insufferably dull in your absence.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005880_ZENOS<tab>Il est grand temps que tu reviennes, mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005890_ZENOS<tab>When you return to me, you will share everything. Every blow will be a story unto itself. Every triumph. Every kill.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005890_ZENOS<tab>J'ai hâte que tu me montres tous les nouveaux tours dont tu es capable... Ils rythmeront le plus sublime combat que cette terre ait jamais connu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005900_ZENOS<tab>Rest assured we shall have a fitting stage for our reunion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005900_ZENOS<tab>Mais avant cela, je dois préparer le théâtre de nos retrouvailles.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005910_ZENOS<tab>Oh, yes. To reprise that transcendent moment, I will set this world ablaze. And we shall dance before the pyre.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005910_ZENOS<tab>Si pour t'affronter dans un duel digne de ce nom, je dois anéantir ce monde tout entier... alors je suis prêt à le faire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005920_GRAHATIA<tab>The beast shall kindle the flames of the apocalypse.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005920_GRAHATIA<tab>Une créaturrre porteuse d'une fin sinistre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005930_GRAHATIA<tab>Into its domain shall the hero set forth, for the final chapter in the tale of this star.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05300_005930_GRAHATIA<tab>Ainsi s'ouvrait un nouveau chapitre pour notre <var 08 E905 ((héroïne)) ((héros)) /var>, la conclusion d'une quête à la crrroisée des astres et des destinées.
